0not%20actively%20recruiting%20drivers%20in%20your%20area%2C%20you%20can%20join%20a%20waitlist%2C%20and%20the%20company%20will%20notify%20you%20when%20positions%20are%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20do%20Flex%20drivers%20earn%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Amazon%20Flex%20app%20description%2C%20most%20delivery%20drivers%20earn%20between%20%2418%20to%20%2425%20per%20hour%2C%20though%20the%20amount%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20your%20location%20and%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20to%20complete%20a%20route.%20The%20program%20allows%20drivers%20to%20set%20their%20own%20schedule%2C%20though%20most%20routes%20take%20between%20two%20and%20six%20hours.%20Drivers%20can%20schedule%20their%20hours%20in%20advance%20or%20request%20same-day%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20Flex%20drivers%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20they%20begin%20a%20shift%2C%20drivers%20use%20the%20Amazon%20Flex%20app%2C%20which%20has%20built-in%20GPS%2C%20to%20track%20and%20navigate%20deliveries.%20Drivers%20can%20search%20for%20a%20delivery%20block%20in%20their%20area%2C%20and%20the%20app%20estimates%20their%20earnings%20and%20how%20long%20the%20block%20should%20take%20to%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20job%20like%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20both%20pros%20and%20cons%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-delivery-drivers-reveal-claims-of-disturbing-work-conditions-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edriving%20for%20Amazon%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Flex.%20As%20its%20name%20indicates%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20flexible%20schedule%20so%20workers%20can%20pick%20up%20as%20many%20or%20as%20few%20routes%20as%20they'd%20like.%20The%20technology%20makes%20the%20job%20relatively%20simple%2C%20according%20to%20one%20driver%20who%20tried%20it%20as%20a%20weekend%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20drivers%20are%20considered%