ou%20make%20quicker%20progress%20toward%20your%20goals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20an%20Amazon%20driver%20or%20fulfillment%20center%20employee%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20experience%2C%20please%20email%20this%20reporter%20at%20jortakales%40insider.com%20or%20text%20(646)%20768-4742%20using%20the%20Signal%20app.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-flex-driver%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699487543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fb281b31c741f0019ac9ed6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-flex-driver%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amazon%20Flex%20drivers%20typically%20earn%20between%20%2418-25%20per%20hour%2C%20and%20shifts%20take%20between%20two%20and%20six%20hours.%20Learn%20what%20the%20delivery%20side%20job%20entails.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jortakales%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-flex-driver%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aliens%20are%20back%20in%20Mexico's%20congress%20chambers%20once%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20a%20presenter%20said%20he%20found%20a%20'new%20species.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224632%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screen%20shows%20what%20a%20Mexican%20journalist%20claims%20are%20aliens%20at%20a%20congressional%20hearing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654c12363cc84b4dfaff16d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223474%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScreen%20shows%20what%20a%20Mexican%20journalist%20claims%20are%20aliens%20at%20a%20congressional%20hearing.%3Cp%3EMarco%20Ugarte%20%2F%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJournalist%20Jos%C3%A9%20Jaime%20Maussan%20again%20testified%20extraterrestrials%20were%20real%20to%20Mexico's%20congress.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20brought%20in%20multiple%20doctors%20who%20said%20the%20specimens%20he%20examined%20were%20real.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20trial%20is%20the%20second%20concerning%20UFOs%20or%20extraterrestrials%20to%20happen%20in%20Mexico's%20congress.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMEXICO%20CITY%20(AP)%20%E2%80%94%20The%20lower%20chamber%20of%20Mexico's%20congress%20once%20again%20turned%20to%20spectacle%20Tuesday%2C%20devoting%20hours%20of%20its%20time%20to%20a%20controversial%20character%20who%20pressed%20the%20case%20for%20%26quot%3Bnon-human%20beings%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20were%20found%20in%20Peru.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20three%20weeks%20after%20Category%205%C2%A0Hurricane%20Otis%C2%A0devastated%20Acapulco%2C%20a%20port%20of%20nearly%201%20million%20people%2C%20the%20Chamber%20of%20Deputies%20spent%20more%20than%20three%20hours%20listening%20to%20journalist%20Jos%C3%A9%20Jaime%20Maussan%20and%20his%20group%20of%20Peruvian%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaussan%2C%C2%A0who%20describes%20himself%20as%20a%20Unidentified%20Anomalous%20Phenomena%20researcher%2C%20and%20some%20Mexican%20lawmakers%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20international%20ridicule%20in%20September%20when%20he%20presented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcongress-testimony-ufos-alien-mummies-et-corpse-ufo-nonhuman-remains-2023-9%5C%22%3Etwo%20boxes%20with%20supposed%20mummies%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20in%20Peru%20at%20Mexico's%20first%20congressional%20hearing%20on%20UFOs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20demonstration%20that%20we%20are%20dealing%20with%20nonhuman%20specimens%20that%20are%20not%20related%20to%20any%20other%20species%20in%20our%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Maussan%20said%20during%20the%20hearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaussan%20claimed%20the%20presented%20figures%20were%20each%20about%201%2C000%20years%20old%2C%20according%20to%20testing%20done%20at%20a%20local%20university%2C%20which%20distanced%20itself%20from%20his%20cause.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Maussan%20made%20similar%20claims%20in%20Peru%2C%20and%20a%20report%20by%20that%20country's%20prosecutor's%20office%20found%20the%20bodies%20were%20actually%20%26quot%3Brecently%20manufactured%20dolls%2C%20which%20have%20been%20covered%20with%20a%20mixture%20of%20paper%20and%20synthetic%20glue%20to%20simulate%20the%20presence%20of%20skin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20the%20figures%20were%20almost%20certainly%20human-made%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthey%20are%20not%20the%20remains%20of%20ancestral%20aliens%20that%20they%20have%20tried%20to%20present.%26quot%3B%20The%20bodies%20were%20not%20publicly%20unveiled%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20it%20is%20unclear%20if%20they%20are%20the%20same%20as%20those%20presented%20to%20Mexico's%20congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Maussan%20insisted%C2%A0the%20Peruvian%20mummies%20from%20the%20September%20hearing%20were%20real%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fmexican-congress-holds-second-ufo-session-featuring-peruvian-mummies-2023-11-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaussan%20brought%20in%20multiple%20doctors%20who%20said%20the%20bodies%20were%20%26quot%3Breal%2C%20once-living%20organisms%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20did%20not%20say%20they%20found%20proof%20that%20the%20mummies%20were%20extraterrestrials%2C%20per%20Reuters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20anthropologist%2C%20Roger%20Zuniga%2C%20told%20Reuters%20he%20didn't%20know%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20beings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuniga%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20absolutely%20no%20human%20intervention%20in%20the%20physical%20and%20biological%20formation%20of%20these%20beings.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20surgeon%20from%20A