2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20five%20of%20Bailey's%20deputies%20were%20convicted%20earlier%20this%20year%20for%20torturing%20and%20sexually%20assaulting%20two%20Black%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20deputies%20called%20themselves%20the%20%26quot%3BGoon%20Squad%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20willingness%20to%20use%20excessive%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20his%20deputies%20are%20now%20in%20jail%2C%20Bailey%20himself%20has%20thus%20far%20avoided%20responsibility.%20And%20now%20he's%20been%20reelected%20for%20another%20term%20after%20an%20uncontested%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBailey%20won%20reelection%20on%20Tuesday%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rankincounty.org%2Fegov%2Fdocuments%2F1699416182_14817.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%2030%2C000%20votes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20there%20was%20no%20official%20entrant%20to%20contest%20the%20election%2C%20more%20than%205%2C000%20people%20voted%20for%20a%20write-in.%20There%20were%20another%206%2C300%20undervotes%2C%20which%20are%20votes%20that%20are%20nullified%20due%20to%20unclear%20markings%20or%20other%20reasons.%20Bailey%20also%20received%20more%20than%2021%2C000%20votes%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rankincounty.org%2Fegov%2Fdocuments%2F1692736773_09764.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprimary%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERankin%20County%2C%20home%20to%20several%20Jackson%20suburbs%2C%20is%20the%20largest%20county%20in%20Mississippi%2C%20with%20a%20population%20of%20almost%20160%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fquickfacts%2Frankincountymississippi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20officers%20who%20called%20themselves%20the%20%26quot%3BGoon%20Squad%26quot%3B%20pleaded%20guilty%20on%20August%203%20to%20federal%20charges%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20two%20Black%20men%20in%20January.%20Five%20were%20deputies%20for%20the%20Rankin%20County%20She