ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-medical-debt-removed-credit-reports-experian-transunion-cfpb-wsj-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20would%20be%20erasing%20nearly%2070%25%20of%20medical%20debt%20from%20their%20customers'%20credit%20reports%2C%20along%20with%20removing%20unpaid%20medical%20debts%20of%20%24500%20or%20less.%20New%20unpaid%20debts%20would%20also%20not%20get%20added%20to%20credit%20reports%20for%20a%20full%20year%20after%20being%20sent%20to%20collections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bureaus%20started%20implementing%20those%20changes%20in%20July%202022%2C%20and%20in%20August%202022%2C%20they%20also%20said%20medical%20debt%20in%20collections%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vantagescore.com%2Fpress_releases%2Fvantagescore-takes-steps-to-further-support-consumers-affected-by-medical-debt-collections%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20be%20used%20to%20calculate%20Vantage%20scores%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20commonly%20used%20credit%20scoring%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20tank%20Urban%20Institute%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.urban.org%2Furban-wire%2Fmedical-debt-was-erased-credit-records-most-consumers-potentially-improving-many%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20analyzing%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20changes%20to%20medical%20debt%20collections.%20Based%20on%20credit%20bureau%20data%2C%20it%20estimated%20that%20more%20than%2015%20million%20consumers%20might%20have%20had%20their%20medical%20debt%20in%20collections%20erased%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20report%20said%20that%20since%20the%20changes%20went%20into%20effect%2C%2027%20million%20consumers%20%26quot%3Bexperienced%20a%20significant%20improvement%20in%20their%20Vantage%20scores.%26quot%3B%20From%20August%202022%20to%20August%202023%2C%20their%20average%20score%20rose%20from%20585%20to%20615