0is%20not%20seeing%20regional%20conflicts%20with%20Iran%20proxies%20escalate%20or%20expand%20the%20conflict%20going%20on%20in%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20crushing%20ISIS%20has%20long%20remained%20a%20focus%20of%20the%20US%20military%2C%20but%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20has%20outlined%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FNews-Stories%2FArticle%2FArticle%2F3581319%2Fus-has-4-objectives-in-middle-east%2F%5C%22%3Efour%20new%20objectives%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%3A%20protecting%20American%20forces%20and%20citizens%2C%20outfitting%20Israel%20with%20security%20assistance%2C%20securing%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20held%20by%20Hamas%2C%20and%20preventing%20the%20war%20from%20spreading%20beyond%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20US%20officials%20stress%20that%20deterrence%20%E2%80%94%20signaled%20by%20the%20massive%20movement%20of%20American%20combat%20power%20into%20the%20region%20%E2%80%94%20is%20working%2C%20and%20the%20Iran-backed%20attacks%20on%20American%20forces%20have%20been%20unsuccessful.%20Future%20retaliation%20is%20not%20off%20the%20table%2C%20but%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20the%20military%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20believe%20that%20it's%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20policymakers%20are%20trying%20to%20keep%20their%20heads%20above%20the%20emotional%20level%20to%20keep%20us%20focused%20and%20moving%20towards%20those%20broader%20objectives%20that%20prevent%20wider%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Lord%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20in%20the%20end%2C%20likely%20will%20serve%20to%20save%20us%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-avoiding-revenge-iran-backed-attacks-troops-middle-east-experts-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699476673000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654b8e8b36d588dc55ccd36c%3