thics%20Committee%2C%20examining%20the%20%26quot%3Bcash-for-query%26quot%3B%20allegations%20against%20Trinamool%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20has%20recommended%20her%20expulsion%20from%20Parliament%20in%20a%20500-page%20report%20accessed%20by%20NDTV.%20She%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20panel%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20look%20back%20at%20the%20case%20so%20far%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20demanded%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20immediate%20suspension%20from%20Parliament%20last%20month%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20taking%20bribes%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20the%20House%20to%20target%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20Adani%20group.%20He%20wrote%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20highlighting%20Ms%20Moitra's%20alleged%20breach%20of%20parliamentary%20privilege%2C%20contempt%20of%20House%2C%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBetween%202019%20and%202023%2C%2050%20of%20the%2061%20questions%20asked%20by%20Ms%20Moitra%20were%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20alleged%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20MP%20gave%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20access%20to%20her%20Lok%20Sabha%20account%20for%20him%20to%20directly%20post%20the%20questions.%20Mr%20Dubey%20cited%20%26quot%3Bpainstaking%20research%26quot%3B%20by%20advocate%20Jai%20Anand%20Dehadrai%2C%20who%20approached%20the%20CBI%20with%20some%20of%20his%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMahua%20Moitra%20rubbished%20all%20allegations%20against%20her%2C%20labelling%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bjilted%20ex%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Dehadrai%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20claimed%20he%20anticipated%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20serious%20threat%20to%20his%20life%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20his%20complaint.%20He%20claimed%20a%20direct%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20coerce%20him%20into%20withdrawing%20his%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENishikant%20Dubey's%20complaint%20to%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20Ethics%20Panel%20of%20Parliament%2C%20which%20called%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20and%20Jai%20Anand%20Dehadrai%20for%20a%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20Dubai-based%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%2C%20in%20an%20explosive%20affidavit%2C%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20indeed%20shared%20her%20parliament%20credentials%20with%20him%20to%20frame%20and%20post%20questions%20on%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20which%20she%20felt%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20target%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Hiranandani%20further%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20was%20%26quot%3Bdominating%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bambitious%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20demanded%20several%20%26quot%3Bfavours%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20expensive%20luxury%20items%2C%20%26quot%3Bproviding%20support%20for%20the%20renovation%20of%20her%20officially%20allotted%20bungalow%20in%20Delhi%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20travel%20and%20holiday%20expenses.%20He%20said%20he%20gave%20in%20to%20her%20demands%20to%20retain%20their%20friendship%20and%20her%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20was%20shredded%20by%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20office%20%26quot%3Bheld%20a%20proverbial%20gun%26quot%3B%20to%20Mr%20Hiranandani's%20head%20to%20make%20him%20sign%20the%20white%20paper%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Bleaked%20to%20the%20press%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20just%20a%20day%20later%2C%20Mr%20Hiranandani%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20news%20channel%2C%20insisted%20that%20he%20had%20not%20filed%20the%20affidavit%20under%20any%20pressure.%20In%20the%20interview%2C%20the%20businessman%20said%20he%20spoke%20up%20since%20the%20%26quot%3Bcash-for-query%26quot%3B%20allegations%20named%20him%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%20and%20personally%26quot%3B%20and%20admitted%20that%20he%20used%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20parliamentary%20login%20ID%20and%20password%20to%20post%20questions%20from%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20took%20a%20surprising%20turn%20when%20Mahua%20Moitra%20admitted%20that%20she%20did%20share%20her%20parliament%20login%20ID%20and%20password%20with%20Mr%20Hiranandani.%20She%20also%20admitted%20to%20receiving%20gifts%20but%20said%20that%20the%20only%20things%20she%20got%20from%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20were%20%26quot%3Bone%20scarf%2C%20some%20lipsticks%2C%20and%20other%20makeup%20items%20including%20eye%20shadow%26quot%3B.%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20taking%20bribes%20from%20him%20and%20demanded%20that%20she%20be%20given%20the%20chance%20to%20cross-examine%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20firebrand%20MP%20refused%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20on%20October%2031%2C%20the%20first%20summons%20she%20got.%20Explaining%20her%20stance%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BChairman%2C%20Ethics%20Comm%20announced%20my%2031%2F10%20summons%20on%20live%20TV%20way%20before%20the%20official%20letter%20was%20emailed%20to%20me%20at%2019%3A20%20hours.%20All%20complaints%20and%20suo%20moto%20affidavits%20were%20also%20released%20to%20the%20media.%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20deposing%20immediately%20after%20my%20pre-scheduled%20constituency%20programmes%20end%20on%20November%204.%26quot%3B%20She%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bselective%20leak%20of%20a%20plea%20bargain%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20was%20part%20of%20the%20establishment's%20%26quot%3Bwitch%20hunt%20into%20every%20political%20leader%20who%20dares%20question%20Adani%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20finally%20appeared%20before%20the%20panel%20on%20November%202%20but%20staged%20a%20walkout%20along%20with%20the%20Opposition%20MPs%2C%20questioning%20the%20way%20the%20meeting%20was%20conducted%20and%20accusing%20the%20panel%20of%20subjecting%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bproverbial%20vastraharan%20(stripping)%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Speaker.%20The%20panel%20shot%20back%20saying%20she%20did%20not%20cooperate%20and%20left%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20answering%20more%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ethics%20committee%20chief%20Vinod%20Sonkar%20said%20Ms%20Moitra%20did%20not%20cooperate%20during%20her%20cross-examination.%20%26quot%3BObjectionable%20words%20were%20used%20against%20the%20panel's%20functioning%20and%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Another%20panel%20member%2C%20Aparajita%20Sarangi%2C%20said%20Ms%20Moitra%20%26quot%3Bbehaved%20in%20an%20angry%2C%20arrogant%20manner%20when%20asked%20about%20Darshan%20Hiranandani's%20affidavit%26quot%3B.%20But%20the%20Opposition%20MPs%20alleged%20that%20the%20committee%20asked%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20and%20unethical%20questions%26quot%3B%20to%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20MPs%20leaked%20details%20of%20the%20meeting%20to%20the%20media%20while%20it%20was%20underway.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20kind%20of%20meeting%20was%20this%3F%20They%20are%20asking%20all%20kinds%20of%20filthy%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20visibly%20upset%20Ms%20Moitra%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20anti-corruption%20body%20Lokpal%2C%20which%20took%20up%20the%20case%20in%20a%20meeting%20and%20approved%20it%2C%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BOn%20basis%20of%20my%20complaint%2C%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20corruption%20that%20compromises%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20BJP%20MP's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETh%20Ethics%20Panel%20will%20meet%20tomorrow%20to%20adopt%20the%20report%20on%20Mahua%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699465020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fin6sfjg_mahua-moitra-pti_625x300_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funethical-conduct-by-mahua-moitra-says-ethics-panel-case-so-far-4558714%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20examining%