y%22%3A%22Social%20media%20giant%20Meta%20has%20announced%20a%20new%20policy%20that%20requires%20advertisers%20to%20disclose%20when%20they%20digitally%20create%20or%20alter%20a%20political%20or%20social%20issue%20ad%20in%20certain%20cases.%20Advertisers%20will%20have%20to%20disclose%20whenever%20an%20ad%20contains%20digitally%20created%20or%20altered%20content%20that%20depicts%20a%20real%20person%20saying%20or%20doing%20something%20they%20did%20not%2C%20or%20depicts%20a%20realistic-looking%20person%20or%20event%20that%20does%20not%20exist.%20The%20move%20comes%20as%20India%20prepares%20for%20elections%20and%20in%20response%20to%20the%20government's%20crackdown%20on%20deep%20fakes%20and%20misinformation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PANKAJ%20DOVAL%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Famidst-controversy-over-deep-fakes-meta-seeks-disclosure-from-advertisers-on-content-changes-through-ai-or-digital-methods%2Farticleshow%2F105075823.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BExpel%20Mahua%20Moitra%20From%20Lok%20Sabha%26quot%3B%3A%20Ethics%20Panel%20In%20500-Page%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress's%20Mahua%20Moitra%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20as%20an%20MP%20and%20her%20membership%20should%20be%20terminated%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20Ethics%20Committee%20examining%20the%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20her%20has%20recommended.%20Calling%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20actions%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20objectionable%2C%20unethical%2C%20heinous%20and%20criminal%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20committee%20said%20it%20calls%20for%20severe%20punishment.%20In%20the%20operative%20part%20of%20the%20500-page%20report%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%2C%20the%20committee%20has%20also%20recommended%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Blegal%2C%20intensive%2C%20institutional%20and%20time-bound%20investigation%26quot%3B%20be%20held%20into%20the%20entire%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20has%20concluded%20that%20Mahua%20Moitra%20had%20shared%20user%20ID%20with%20%26quot%3Bunauthorised%20persons%26quot%3B%2C%20took%20cash%20and%20amenities%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20and%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bserious%20misdemeanour%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20part%20which%20calls%20for%20%26quot%3Bserious%20punishment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20money%20trail%20of%20cash%20transaction%20between%20Smt%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20Shri%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20'quid%20pro%20quo'%20should%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20in%20a%20legal%2C%20institutional%20and%20time-bound%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20will%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20during%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament%20and%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20after%20a%20discussion.%20Ms%20Moitra%20is%20expected%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20committee%20at%204%20pm%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20had%20stormed%20out%20of%20the%20last%20meeting%2C%20held%20last%20week%2C%20objecting%20to%20their%20questions%20and%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Speaker%2C%20accused%20the%20committee%20of%20subjecting%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bproverbial%20%3Cem%3Evastraharan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(stripping)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ethics%20panel%20chief%20--%20BJP%20MP%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar%20--%20had%20focussed%20on%20Ms%20Moitra's%20personal%20relationship%20with%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%20There%20were%20questions%20too%20on%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%2C%20on%20whose%20complaint%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20the%20entire%20case%20rests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20has%20accused%20Ms%20Moitra%20of%20failing%20to%20cooperate.%20%26quot%3BMahua%20Moitra%20did%20not%20cooperate%20with%20the%20committee%20and%20the%20investigation.%20The%20Opposition%20members%20also%20made%20allegations%20in%20anger%20and%20suddenly%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%20to%20avoid%20answering%20more%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sonkar%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20%E2%80%93%20who%20had%20flagged%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20--%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20that%20anti-corruption%20body%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20into%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20basis%20of%20my%20complaint%2C%20Lokpal%20has%20ordered%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20corruption%20that%20compromises%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20rough%20translation%20of%20the%20post%20by%20Mr%20Dubey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MP%20had%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20accepted%20cash%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%20on%20his%20behalf%20to%20target%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20business%20rival%20Adani%20Group.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20by%20sharing%20her%20parliamentary%20login%20with%20the%20businessman%2C%20has%20compromised%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20had%20admitted%20to%20it%2C%20but%20claimed%20there%20is%20no%20regulation%20governing%20sharing%20of%20login%20and%20password.%20Ahead%20of%20her%20hearing%20with%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20she%20had%20written%20them%20a%20letter%2C%20questioning%20%26quot%3BWhy%20these%20rules%20are%20not%20shared%20with%20MPs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20explosive%20affidavit%20last%20month%2C%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20admitted%20to%20the%20login%20sharing%2C%20but%20bypassed%20the%20cash%20for%20query%20issue%2C%20saying%20they%20shared%20a%20close%20friendship%20and%20he%20had%20given%20Ms%20Moitra%20gifts%20that%20she%20had%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%2