rtment.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20haven't%20received%20any%20order%20from%20transport%20department%2C%20we%20want%20to%20reiterate%20that%20all%20the%20cars%20on%20the%20Uber%20platform%20in%20Delhi%20are%20CNG%20or%20electric%20and%20shared%20mobility%20helps%20more%20people%20commute%20in%20fewer%20cars%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Uber%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndustry%20sources%20too%20said%20there%20is%20no%20official%20order%20from%20transport%20department%20at%20the%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20plans%20to%20present%20two%20studies%20before%20the%20top%20court%20on%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20odd-even%20road%20rationing%20--%20scheduled%20to%20begin%20after%20Diwali%20--%20the%20minister%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%20These%20include%20a%20joint%20study%20by%20the%20Harvard%20and%20Chicago%20State%20University%20in%20the%20US%20and%20one%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Technical%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20hearing%20yesterday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20called%20schemes%20like%20odd-even%20a%20matter%20of%20%26quot%3Bmere%20optics%26quot%3B%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20consider%20allowing%20cabs%20on%20roads%20that%20have%20Delhi%20registration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20also%20note%20that%20there%20is%20a%20large%20number%20of%20the%20App%20based%20taxis%20in%20Delhi%20which%20have%20registrations%20in%20different%20States.%20If%20we%20look%20at%20the%20roads%2C%20each%20one%20is%20carrying%20only%20one%20passenger%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20said%2C%20asking%20the%20state%20if%20it%20could%20stop%20it%20as%20an%20additional%20step%20to%20control%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESlamming%20the%20odd-even%20scheme%20already%20announced%2C%20the%20court%20questioned%20if%20there%20is%20any%20study%20to%20back%20up%20such%20a%20move.%20%26quot%3BHave%20you%20evaluated%20how%20it%20worked%20in%20previous%20years%3F%20Such%20schemes%20are%20only%20optics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20judges%2C%20who%20were%20hearing%20a%20petition%20on%20the%20rising%20pollution.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20has%20said%20the%20scheme%20will%20be%20implemented%20once%20the%20court%20reviews%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20week%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20had%20dropped%20abysmally.%20The%20locals%20have%20been%20waking%20up%20to%20a%20thick%20haze%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20noxious%20particulate%20matter%20has%20been%20seen%20to%20be%20four%20times%20the%20permissible%20limit%20in%20many%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20satellite%20pictures%20showed%20a%20massive%20black%20plume%20of%20smoke%20covering%20the%20entire%20north%20India.%20A%20big%20contributor%20were%20the%20fields%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20where%20stubble%20burning%20is%20an%20annual%20ritual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20underscored%20the%20need%20to%20stop%20stubble%20burning%20%E2%80%93%20a%20tricky%20issue%20for%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20which%20governs%20both%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20it%20stopped.%20We%20don't%20know%20how%20you%20do%20it%2C%20it's%20your%20job.%20But%20it%20must%20be%20stopped.%20Something%20has%20to%20be%20done%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699461000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F7ohqig2o_delhi-pollution-sondeep_625x300_08_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-bans-entry-of-app-based-taxis-from-other-states-as-air-quality-dips-4557824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22App-based%20cabs%20from%20other%20states%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20Delhi%20under%20yesterday's%20Supreme%20Court%20suggestion%20meant%20to%20curb%20the%20annual%2C%20spiralling%20pollution%2C%20said%20state%20Transport%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai.%22%2C%22author%22