0in%20Parel%2C%20where%20he%20was%20kept%20in%20an%20incubator%20for%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkshay%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cerebral%20palsy%2C%20a%20neurological%20condition%20that%20affects%20movement%20and%20muscle%20coordination.%20He%20had%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20physiotherapy%20daily%20since%20then.%20As%20Ravindra%20was%20working%20in%20a%20bank%2C%20Sujata%20took%20on%20this%20responsibility.%20She%20would%20carry%20her%20month-old%20baby%20%E2%80%94%20who%20hardly%20weighed%20a%20kilo%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Badlapur%20to%20Parel%20everyday%20for%20therapy%2C%20in%20hopes%20of%20providing%20him%20with%20a%20chance%20to%20have%20a%20better%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20journey%20of%20the%20mother%20and%20son%20continued%20for%20the%20first%20seven%20years%20of%20his%20life.%20But%20these%20daily%20train%20rides%20while%20lifting%20a%20young%20boy%20were%20taxing%20for%20Sujata%2C%20who%20is%2061%20today.%20She%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20a%20better%20way%3B%20there%20had%20to%20be%20a%20better%20way%20to%20help%20her%20son.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20found%20our%20calling%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20853px)%20100vw%2C%20853px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20are%20engaged%20in%20art%2C%20craft%2C%20games%20and%20other%20activities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859.jpeg%20853w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859-768x1152.jpeg%2