20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sujata.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20the%20apprehensions%2C%20hopes%2C%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%20of%20parents%20of%20a%20child%20with%20disabilities.%20We%20will%20help%20your%20children%20fly%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ravindra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThey%20are%20in%20urgent%20need%20of%20funds.%20If%20you%20wish%20to%20donate%2C%20here%20are%20their%20account%20details%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccount%20Transfer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBank%3A%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccount%20no%3A%201955000100007181%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIFSC%3A%20PUNB0609800%20(Ambernath%20Branch)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonate%20via%20UPI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENumber%3A%20%2B91-9867845469%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUPI%20ID%3A%209867845469%40okbizaxis%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699457058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333887%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravindra%20and%20Sujata%20Sugwekar%20were%20motivated%20by%20their%20son%2C%20who%20has%20cerebral%20palsy%2C%20to%20provide%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20other%20children%20with%20disabilities.%20They%20run%20Sangopita%2C%20a%20shelter%20home%2C%20in%20Thane%2C%20to%20help%20them%20flourish.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20500%20Ranking%2C%20No%20Online%20Class%3A%20Rules%20For%20Foreign%20Universities%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20on%20Wednesday%20notified%20the%20regulations%20for%20foreign%20universities%20to%20set%20up%20and%20operate%20their%20campuses%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20regulations%20aim%20to%20facilitate%20the%20entry%20of%20Foreign%20Higher%20Educational%20Institutions%20(FHEIs)%20into%20India%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20NEP%20recommendations%20and%20to%20provide%20an%20international%20dimension%20to%20higher%20education%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20regulations%20aim%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20education%20imparted%20in%20the%20(India)%20campus%20is%20at%20par%20with%20that%20of%20the%20main%20campus%20in%20the%20country%20of%20origin%20and%20that%20its%20operations%20comply%20with%20the%20applicable%20laws%20and%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20UGC%20Chairman%20M%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20regulations%2C%20%26quot%3BForeign%20institutions%20intending%20to%20establish%20campuses%20in%20India%20should%20have%20secured%20a%20position%20within%20the%20top%20500%20in%20the%20overall%20category%20of%20global%20rankings%2C%20as%20decided%20by%20the%20commission%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20or%20should%20have%20secured%20a%20position%20within%20the%20top%20500%20in%20the%20subject-wise%20category%20of%20global%20rankings%20and%20should%20possess%20outstanding%20expertise%20in%20a%20particular%20area%2C%20as%20decided%20by%20the%20commission%20from%20time%20to%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20an%20FHEI%20desires%20to%20receive%20or%20utilise%20foreign%20contributions%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20obtain%20registration%20or%20prior%20permission%20under%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act%2C%202010%20and%20comply%20with%20legal%20requirement%20under%20the%20FCRA%2C%20the%20UGC%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20Indian%20campuses%2C%20foreign%20universities%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20offer%20study%20programmes%20leading%20to%20the%20award%20of%20certificates%2C%20diplomas%2C%20degrees%2C%20research%20and%20other%20programmes%20at%20the%20undergraduate%2C%20postgraduate%2C%20doctoral%20and%20post-doctoral%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForeign%20universities%20cannot%20open%20learning%20centres%2C%20study%20centres%2C%20or%20franchises%20that%20may%20act%20as%20representative%20offices%20of%20the%20parent%20entity%20to%20undertake%20promotional%20activities%20for%20their%20programmes%20in%20their%20home%20jurisdiction%20or%20any%20other%20jurisdiction%20outside%20India.%20They%20are%20required%20to%20seek%20prior%20approval%20from%20the%20commission%20before%20starting%20any%20new%20programme%20in%20their%20campus%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20regulations%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20programmes%20can%20be%20offered%20online%20or%20in%20Open%20and%20Distance%20Learning%20modes%20under%20these%20regulations.%20However%2C%20lectures%20in%20online%20mode%20not%20exceeding%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20programme%20requirements%20are%20allowed%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20or%20more%20than%20two%20universities%20can%20collaborate%20to%20set%20up%20campuses%20in%20India%2C%20provided%20each%20institution%20meets%20the%20eligibility%20criteria%20individually.%20Each%20foreign%20university%20can%20set%20up%20more%20than%20one%20campus%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20they%20shall%20make%20a%20separate%20application%20for%20each%20proposed%20campus%20to%20the%20commission%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20regulations%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForeign%20institutions%20need%20not%20pay%20any%20annual%20fees%20to%20the%20UGC%20other%20than%20the%20one-time%20application%20fees.%20They%20shall%20set%20up%20their%20campuses%20using%20their%20own%20infrastructure%2C%20land%2C%20physical%20resources%20and%20human%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForeign%20universities%20may%20provide%20in%20their%20Indian%20campuses%20full%20or%20partial%20merit-based%20or%20need-based%20scholarships%20and%20fee%20concessions%20to%20Indian%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForeign%20Higher%20Educational%20Institutions%20can%20admit%