s%252C%2520etc%252C.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edivision%20to%20tackle%20LWE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20was%20created%20in%202006%2C%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20role%20is%20to%20deal%20with%20it%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cholistic%20manner%E2%80%9D%20while%20the%20primary%20responsibility%20lies%20with%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20dealing%20with%20this%20decades-old%20problem%2C%20it%20has%20been%20felt%20appropriate%2C%20after%20various%20high-level%20deliberations%20and%20interactions%20with%20the%20State%20Governments%20concerned%2C%20that%20an%20integrated%20approach%20aimed%20at%20the%20relatively%20more%20affected%20areas%20would%20deliver%20results.%20With%20this%20in%20view%2C%20a%20detailed%20analysis%20of%20the%20spread%20and%20trends%20in%20respect%20of%20Left%20Wing%20Extremist%20violence%20has%20been%20made%20and%2070%20districts%20in%20ten%20States%20have%20been%20taken%20up%20for%20special%20attention%20with%20regard%20to%20planning%2C%20implementation%20and%20monitoring%20various%20interventions.%20However%2C%20%E2%80%98Police%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Public%20Order%E2%80%99%20being%20State%20subjects%2C%20action%20on%20maintenance%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%20lies%20primarily%20in%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20State%20Governments.%20The%20Central%20Government%20closely%20monitors%20the%20situation%20and%20supplements%20and%20coordinates%20their%20efforts%20in%20several%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20efforts%20include%20providing%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPFs)%3B%20sanction%20of%20India%20Reserve%20(IR)%20battalions%3B%20setting%20up%20of%20Counter%20Insurgency%20and%20Anti-Terrorism%20(CIAT)%20schools%3B%20modernisation%20and%20upgradation%20of%20the%20State%20Police%20and%20their%20Intelligence%20apparatus%3B%20reimbursement%20of%20security-related%20expenditure%20under%20the%20Security-related%20Expenditure%20(SRE