hary%20is%20still%20alive%20and%20living%20in%20the%20Nikol%20area%20under%20a%20new%20name%2C%20Rajkumar%20Chaudhry%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20arrest%2C%20Anilsingh%20Chaudhary%20admitted%20he%20and%20his%20father%20had%20hatched%20a%20plan%20to%20usurp%20accident%20insurance%20money%20by%20staging%20his%20death.%20As%20per%20the%20plan%2C%20Anilsingh%20Chaudhary%20took%20an%20accidental%20death%20insurance%20policy%20in%202004%20and%20then%20purchased%20a%20car%2C%20said%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Anilsingh%20Chaudhary%2C%20his%20father%20and%20brothers%20lured%20a%20beggar%2C%20who%20begged%20for%20alms%20in%20trains%2C%20with%20an%20offer%20of%20food.%20They%20took%20the%20beggar%20to%20a%20hotel%20near%20Agra%20and%20served%20him%20food%20laced%20with%20sedatives%2C%20said%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20then%20dumped%20the%20unconscious%20beggar%20in%20their%20car%20and%20deliberately%20rammed%20the%20vehicle%20against%20an%20electricity%20pole%20to%20portray%20it%20like%20an%20accident.%20They%20subsequently%20placed%20the%20beggar%20on%20the%20driver's%20seat%20and%20set%20the%20car%20ablaze%20to%20show%20the%20vehicle%20caught%20fire%20due%20to%20the%20accident%2C%20said%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnilsingh%20Chaudhary's%20father%20Vijaypalsingh%20identified%20the%20body%20as%20that%20of%20his%20son%20and%20cremated%20it%20in%20his%20native%20village%20in%20Gautam%20Buddha%20Nagar%20district.%20As%20per%20the%20plan%2C%20Vijaypalsingh%20Chaudhary%20claimed%20Rs%2080%20lakh%20in%20accidental%20death%20insurance%20of%20his%20son%20and%20distributed%20the%20sum%20among%20family%20members%2C%20said%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20collecting%20his%20share%2C%20Anilsingh%20Chaudhary%20came%20to%20Ahmedabad%20in%202006%20and%20never%20went%20back%20to%20his%20native%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20said%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20changed%20his%20name%20to%20Rajkumar%