20last%20fortnight%20owing%20to%20his%2016-wicket%20burst%20over%20four%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShami%20is%20an%20apex%20predator%2C%20zooming%20in%20on%20the%20stumps%20and%20hunting%20for%20wickets%20all%20the%20time.%20Perhaps%2C%20no%20other%20contemporary%20bowler%20hit%20the%20timber%20as%20often%20as%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Bumrah%20has%20a%20totally%20different%20philosophy%2C%20something%20that%20will%20thrill%20the%20connoisseurs%20more.%20He%20likes%20to%20build%20up%20pressure%20with%20dot%20balls%20and%20draw%20batsmen%20into%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECheck%20this%20piece%20of%20statistics.%20Bumrah%20has%20an%20economy%20of%203.65%20across%20eight%20matches%20and%20it%20is%20the%20best%20among%20bowlers%20who%20have%20played%20at%20least%20two%20games%20in%20this%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20showpiece%2C%20the%20average%20run-rate%20in%20the%20first%20Power%20Play%20(1-10%20overs)%20hovers%20around%20six%2C%20but%20Bumrah's%20economy%20stands%20at%20a%20thrifty%202.9%20during%20this%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20like%20a%20python%20grip.%20He%20just%20doesn't%20give%20any%20breathing%20space%20to%20the%20batters%20just%20as%20he%20had%20restricted%20a%20free-flowing%20Gill%20on%20this%20day%20at%20nets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%2C%20being%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20pack%20prompts%20Bumrah%20not%20to%20chase%20wickets%20but%20him%20building%20pressure%20at%20one%20end%20allows%20the%20likes%20of%20Shami%20or%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kuldeep%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63624-kuldeep-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20feed%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20that%20Bumrah%20is%20incapable%20of%20moments%20of%20magic.%20He%20can%20bring%20out%20that%20dreaded%20yorker%20at%20will%2C%20like%20the%20one%20crashed%20on%20to%20the%20base%20of%20Bangladesh%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mahmudullah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3