nergy-system-60-times-ahead-of-winter-kyiv%2Famp_articleshow%2F105073480.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Disabled%20People%20in%20India%2C%20Securing%20Health%20Insurance%20Is%20Still%20a%20Difficult%20Task%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08185756%2Fimage-1488.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arman%20Ali%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Employment%20for%20Disabled%20People%20(NCPEDP)%2C%20secured%20health%20insurance%20in%20mid-October%20after%20a%20seven-year%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%2C%20who%20uses%20a%20wheelchair%2C%20is%20one%20of%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccdisabilities.nic.in%2Fresources%2Fdisability-india%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520India%2520out%2520of%2520the%2C2.21%2525%2520of%2520the%2520total%2520population.%5C%22%3E27%20million%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20who%20live%20with%20disabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20disabled%20population%20in%20India%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20affordable%20healthcare%20services%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20NCPEDP%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20has%20been%20advocating%20for%20the%20healthcare%20rights%20of%20people%20with%20disabilities%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecuring%20health%20insurance%20is%20a%20significant%20step%20toward%20affordability.%20But%20in%20India%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20disability%2C%20the%20more%20difficult%20it%20becomes%20to%20gain%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20uses%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccdisabilities.nic.in%2Factsguideline%2Fguidelines-evaluation-various-disabilities-and-procedure-certification%5C%22%3Erating%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20evaluate%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20degree%20of%20disability.%20Per%20this%20system%2C%20Ali%E2%80%99s%20degree%20of%20disability%20is%2080%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20over%20the%20past%20seven%20years%2C%20he%20has%20made%20several%20attempts%20to%20apply%20for%20insurance%2C%20but%20was%20met%20with%20rejections%20and%20no%20explanations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20gone%20through%20tests%2C%20given%20all%20my%20papers%20and%20documents%2C%20handed%20it%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20and%20they%20denied%20it%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20me%20an%20explanation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20that%E2%80%99s%20very%20painful.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20it%E2%80%99s%20going%20wrong%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20disability%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20health%20condition%2C%20and%20so%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08185510%2Fimage-1487.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22606%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08185510%2Fimage-1487.png%20606w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08185510%2Fimage-1487-220x300.png%20220w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22826%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20for%20assistive%20technology%20like%20Ali%E2%80%99s%20wheelchair%20is%20a%20problem%2C%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Ftools%2Fata-toolkit%5C%22%3EThe%20WHO%20Global%20Report%20on%20Assistive%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%202.5%20billion%20people%20globally%20require%20assistive%20technology.%20It%20said%20that%20while%20data%20is%20limited%2C%20in%20Africa%20and%20Asia%2C%20surveys%20showed%20largely%20unmet%20needs%2C%20ranging%20from%2025%25%20to%20over%2090%25%20due%20to%20high%20costs%2C%20lack%20of%20financing%2C%20availability%2C%20awareness%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20trained%20personnel.%20These%20unmet%20needs%20are%20only%20heightened%20by%20the%20difficulty%20in%20getting%20assistive%20technology%20insured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20finally%20secured%20insurance%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20coverage%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fcompany%2Fstar-health-and-allied-insurance-co--ltd%2F%5C%22%3EStar%20Health%20and%20Allied%20Insurance%20Co.%20Ltd%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20private%20insurance%20company%2C%20and%20got%20his%20wheelchair%20insured%20under%20the%20all-risk%20cover%20policy%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fcompany%2Fsbigeneral%2F%5C%22%3ESBI%20General%20Insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20coverage%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmomentous%20step%20forward%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20his%20insurance%20would%20cover%20his%20assistive%20technology%20needs%20and%20services%20like%20rehabilitation%20and%20physiotherapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20gaining%20insurance%20for%20his%20wheelchair%20instils%20hope%20and%20inspiration%20for%20the%20millions%20of%20people%20with%20disabilities%20and%20elderly%20people%20who%20use%20a%20variety%20of%20assistive%20devices%20for%20their%20activities%20of%20daily%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20sent%20emails%20and%20letters%20to%20the%20managing%20directors%20and%20CEOs%20of%2026%20public%20and%20private%20general%20insurance%20companies%2C%20but%20received%20no%20response%20from%20almost%2040%25%20of%20the%20companies.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20received%20an%20offer%20from%20SBI%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoor%20response%20from%20government%20hospitals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20that%20discrimination%20in%20accessing%20healthcare%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20terms%20of%20response%2C%20government%20insurance%20companies%20perform%20the%20poorest.%20They%20did%20not%20get%20back%20to%20him%20despite%20multiple%20follow-ups%20from%20other%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20despite%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20saying%20that%20insurance%20products%20should%20be%20designed%20to%20enable%20people%20with%20disabilities%20to%20obtain%20health%20insurance%20coverage%20and%20that%20people%20with%20disabilities%20cannot%20be%20discriminated%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20he%20hopes%20to%20instil%20hope%20among%20many%20people%20by%20sharing%20the%20news%20of%20his%20health%20insurance%20coverage.%20He%20believes%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20acute%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20disabled%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20navigate%20the%20process%20of%20obtaining%20insurance%20and%20it%20becomes%20a%20huge%20cost%20for%20the%20families%20and%20disabled%20people%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20said%20this%20lack%20of%20understanding%20extends%20to%20insurance%20companies%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20need%20to%20build%20awareness%20%5Bon%20insurance%20products%20for%20disabled%20people%5D%2C%20and%20the%20government%20should%20also%20incentivise%20or%20come%20up%20with%20schemes%20that%20include%20all%20people%20with%20disabilities%20under%20Ayushman%20Bharat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20challenges%20around%20understanding%20blood%20disorders%20and%20insurance%20will%20not%20be%20resolved%20until%20and%20unless%20we%20build%20our%20understanding%20around%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20NCPEDP%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20and%20Insurance%20Regulatory%20Development%20Authority%20of%20India%20(IRDAI)%20held%20a%20stakeholders%20consultation%20with%20disability%20advocacy%20organisations%20in%20Mumbai%20where%20he%20said%20both%20private%20and%20government%20insurance%20companies%20were%20present.%3C%2F