0other%20members%20Nripendra%20Mishra%20and%20Anil%20Mishra%20while%20Mahant%20Kamalnayan%20Das%2C%20Ramanand%20Das%20and%20Maithili%20Kishori%20Sharan%20of%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Ramanandi%20sect%20have%20been%20appointed%20as%20guest%20members.%20This%20committee%20will%20get%20the%20%3Cem%3Epuja%3C%2Fem%3E%20rituals%20transcribed%20under%20its%20supervision%20and%20publish%20them%20in%20a%20book%2C%20so%20that%20there%20is%20no%20ambiguity%20at%20any%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20news%20about%20the%20Trust%E2%80%99s%20decision%20broke%2C%20experts%20began%20speculating%20how%20far%20this%20chalk-and-cheese%20combination%20of%20Ramanandi%20sect%2C%20known%20for%20establishing%20coordination%20between%20different%20streams%20and%20branches%20of%20Rambhakti%2C%20preaching%20against%20caste%20hatred%20and%20nurturing%20pluralism%2C%20and%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%2C%20which%20is%20dominated%20by%20a%20particular%20caste%2C%20will%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%20650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-629759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20for%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20since%20its%20formation%2C%20the%20Trust%20has%20been%20in%20the%20dock%20for%20inadequate%20and%20zero%20representation%20of%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20castes.%20Pluralism%20%E2%80%93%20the%20essence%20of%20this%20country%20%E2%80%93%20with%20its%20diversity%20of%20opinions%20(as%20also%20of%20its%20majority%20Hindus)%2C%20is%20completely%20absent%20from%20the%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20leaders%20of%20the%20above-mentioned%20castes%20allege%20that%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20used%20them%20extensively%20in%20the%20movement%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20%E2%80%98there%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20once%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98successful%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20were%20denied%20even%20the%20slightest%20share%20in%20the%20credit%20for%20the%20success.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20what%20can%20one%20say%20about%20those%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20Harijans%E2%80%99%2C%20whom%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect%20had%20welcomed%20with%20open%20arms%20when%20it%20was%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20and%20who%20were%20the%20target%20of%20malicious%20hatred%20widely%20spread%20by%20the%20VHP%20during%20the%20temple%20movement%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fram-janmabhoomi-trust-ayodhya-controversy-again%5C%22%3EAyodhya%3A%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20Stirs%20Controversy%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERamanandi%20sect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20of%20the%20Trust%2C%20however%2C%20did%20arouse%20curiosity%20about%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect.%20This%20largest%20sect%20of%20Vaishnav%20sadhus%20and%20ascetics%20in%20the%20country%20was%20started%20in%20the%20medieval%20period%20by%20Swami%20Ramanand%20(respectfully%20addressed%20by%20his%20followers%20as%20Swami%20Jagatguru%20Shri%20Ramanandacharya).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08173851%2FStamp_of_India_-_2002_-_Colnect_158243_-_Swami_Ramanand.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22301%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684143%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22392%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStamp%20issued%20in%20honour%20of%20Swami%20Ramanand.%20Photo%3A%20Government%20of%20India%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20GODL%20License%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20sect%20accepts%20the%20Vishishtadvaita%20theory%20of%20%E2%80%98mukti%E2%80%99%20(which%20is%20defined%20as%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20world%20of%20Ram)%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20four%20oldest%20sects%20of%20Bairagi%20sadhus.%20The%20sect%20is%20also%20referred%20to%20as%20Bairagi%2C%20Ramavat%2C%20and%20Shri%20Sampradaya%20and%20believes%20in%20Paramopasya%20Dwibhujram%20as%20Brahma%20while%20its%20basic%20mantra%20is%20%E2%80%98Om%20Ramay%20Namah%E2%80%99.%20Along%20with%20various%20incarnations%20of%20Vishnu%2C%20they%20worship%20Sita%20and%20Hanuman%20as%20well%2C%20but%20consider%20the%20grace%20of%20both%20Ram%20and%20Vishnu%20indispensable%20for%20salvation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20other%20saviour%20besides%20them%20(Ram%20and%20Vishnu).%20Therefore%2C%20rituals%20are%20not%20given%20much%20importance%20but%20emphasis%20is%20laid%20on%20the%20followers%20being%20generous%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20coordinated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20followers%20of%20the%20sect%20also%20consider%20Ramanand%20to%20be%20an%20incarnation%20of%20Rama.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20serious%20differences%20of%20opinion%20among%20scholars%20regarding%20the%20date%20and%20time%20of%20Ramanand%E2%80%99s%20birth.%20It%20is%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20born%20in%20Allahabad%2C%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20grew%20up%2C%20his%20religious%20parents%20sent%20him%20to%20the%20Shrimath%20located%20at%20Panchgangaghat%20of%20Swami%20Raghvanand%20of%20Kashi%20to%20study%20the%20scriptures.%20After%20completing%20the%20cycle%20of%20study%20and%20meditation%20under%20the%20discipleship%20of%20Swami%20Raghavananda%2C%20he%20set%20out%20on%20a%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20Shrimath%20after%20gaining%20more%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20from%20various%20pilgrimages%20across%20the%20country%2C%20many%20of%20his%20fellow%20disciples%20refused%20to%20sit%20in%20his%20company%20and%20eat%20food%20with%20him%20presuming%20that%20he%20might%20have%20eaten%20food%20made%20or%20touched%20by%20impure%20hands%20during%20the%20wayfaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20matter%20escalated%2C%20Guru%20Raghavanand%20ordered%20Ramanand%20to%20start%20a%20new%20sect%20as%20per%20his%20wisdom.%20According%20to%20some%20experts%2C%20this%20order%20of%20Guru%20Raghavanand%20was%20a%20punishment%20to%20Ramanand%2C%20or%20he%20could%20have%20ordered%20his%20fellow%20disciples%20to%20eat%20with%20Ramanand%20instead.%20But%20it%20does%20not%20seem%20true%20because%20in%20many%20ways%20Swami%20Raghavanand%20was%20also%20an%20egalitarian%20and%20taught%20students%20of%20all%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ramanand%20accepted%20his%20Guru%E2%80%99s%20orders%20and%20never%20looked%20back.%20When%20he%20started%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect%2C%20he%20welcomed%20everyone%20to%20protest%20against%20how%20he%20was%20treated%20as%20an%20untouchable%20by%20his%20fellow%20disciples.%20In%20his%20preaching%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20cares%20about%20caste%20or%20creed%2C%20if%20you%20worship%20Hari%2C%20you%20belong%20to%20Hari.%E2%80%9D%20The%20path%20of%20surrender%20to%20God%20is%20open%20to%20everyone%20and%20a%20person%20of%20any%20caste%20or%20varna%20can%20take%20Ram-mantra%20from%20him%2C%20he%20said.%20Kabir%20also%20borrowed%20this%20mantra%20from%20him%20in%20a%20unique%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Ramanand%20accepted%20Brahmins%2C%20Kshatriyas%2C%20Vaishyas%2C%20Shudras%2C%20women%2C%20and%20Muslims%20among%20his%20disciples.%20Almost%20all%20caste-based%20prejudices%20were%20called%20ignorant%20practices%20and%20eliminated%20while%20efforts%20were%20made%20to%20bridge%20the%20gaps%20created%20due%20to%20hatred%20with%20love%20and%20equality.%20These%20efforts%20later%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20dealing%20with%20Hindu-Muslim%20animosity%2C%20Shaiva-Vaishnav%20dispute%2C%20caste%20hatred%2C%20differences%20of%20opinion%2C%20and%20social%20bitterness%20arising%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProminent%20disciples%20of%20Ramananda%20included%20Kabirdas%2C%20Raidas%20(Ravidas)%2C%20Narharyananda%20(Narharidas)%2C%20Anantananda%2C%20Bhavananda%2C%20Surasari%2C%20Padmavati%2C%20Nabhadas%2C%20Dhanna%20(Jatt)%2C%20Sena%20(Naai)%2C%20Pipasen%20(Rajput)%20and%20Sadna%20(Qasai).%20Among%20them%2C%20Narharyanand%20became%20Narharidas%20after%20taking%20%3Cem%3Ediksha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20being%20initiated%20by%20him%20and%20he%20is%20considered%20the%20guru%20of%20Sant%20Tulsidas.%20Not%20only%20was%20he%20a%20devout%20poet%20and%20saint%20he%20also%20had%20good%20knowledge%20of%20Sanskrit%20and%20Persian%20along%20with%20Brijbhasha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20major%20reason%20why%20Ramanand%20is%20counted%20among%20the%20greatest%20saints%20of%20the%20Bhakti%20movement%20is%20that%20he%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20bring%20Rama%20%3Cem%3Ebhakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20the%20sacred%20heights%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20to%20the%20huts%20of%20the%20poor.%20Also%2C%20to%20fulfil%20the%20duty%20of%20protecting%20it%2C%20he%20equipped%20the%20Bairagi%20Sadhus%20with%20weapons%20and%20organised%20them%20as%20Ani%2C%20or%20army%2C%20and%20got%20many%20of%20their%20Akharas%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20first%20Acharya%20who%20brought%20the%20bhakti%20tradition%20that%20originated%20in%20the%20Dravidian%20region%20in%20the%20south%20to%20north%20India.%20An%20example%20of%20his%20wide%20acceptance%20is%20that%20among%20his%20disciples%2C%20there%20were%20both%20%3Cem%3Enirgunopasakas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Esagunopasakas%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Rama.%20His%20disciples%20like%20Kabir%20and%20Raidas%20took%20a%20different%20path%2C%20especially%20Kabir%20who%20went%20on%20to%20preach%20%E2%80%98One%20Rama%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Dasharatha%2C%20One%20Rama%20dwells%20at%20every%20%3Cem%3Eghat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20One%20Rama%20spans%20the%20world%2C%20One%20Rama%20is%20beyond%20the%20world%E2%80%99%2C%20yet%20they%20accepted%20him%20as%20their%20Guru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2016th%20century%2C%20Saint%20Agradas%2C%20the%20fourth%20generation%20of%20Ramanand%E2%80%99s%20disciple%20tradition%2C%20started%20the%20Rasik%20sect%20and%20many%20saints%20and%20mahants%20of%20Lord%20Rama%E2%80%99s%20Ayodhya%20were%20influenced%20by%20it.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20disciples%20of%20Ramanand%20was%20Anantanand%2C%20whose%20disciple%20Krishnadas%20Payhari%20later%20became%20the%20initiation%20guru%20of%20Queen%20Balabai%20of%20King%20Prithviraj%20of%20Amer.%20Agradas%20was%20the%20disciple%20of%20Krishnadas%20Payahari.%20Therefore%2C%20many%20scholars%20see%20his%20Rasik%20sect%20as%20a%20new%20branch%20of%20the%20Ramanandi%20sect%20and%20also%20as%20a%20synonym%20of%20the%20Sakhi%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Rasik%20sect%2C%20not%20only%20is%20Lord%20Rama%20referred%20to%20as%20Ras%20Bihari%20and%20Kanak%20Bihari%2C%20but%20he%20is%20also%20%E2%80%98Anandkand%2C%20Dashrathananda%2C%20Deenbandhu%2C%20Darun%20Bhavabhayahari%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Navakanj%20Lochan%20Kanjmukh%20Karkanj%20Padakanjarunam%E2%80%99.%20He%20is%20also%20depicted%20as%20%E2%80%98Kandarp%20Aganit%20Amit%20Chhavi%20Navnil%20Neerad%20Sundaram%E2%80%99.%20Rama%20being%20the%20archer%2C%20Dinesh%20and%20the%20demon%20Daityavansh%20Nikandanam%20come%20later%20in%20this%20sect.%20As%20a%20sign%20of%20worship%2C%20he%20is%20sometimes%20portrayed%20sitting%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Ephool%20bangla%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20a%20swing.%20The%20Hindu%20month%20of%20Sawan%20is%20celebrated%20as%20his%20%3Cem%3Ejhoolanotsav%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20festival%20of%20swings%20%E2%80%93%20and%20month-long%20fairs%20are%20organised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20this%20depiction%2C%20in%20the%20Ramlilas%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20Ravana%20or%20conquering%20Lanka%2C%20Rama%E2%80%99s%20archer%20or%20warrior%20form%20is%20compulsorily%20shown%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20tradition%20of%20any%20major%20festival%20or%20fair%20on%20that%20day.%20Fairs%20are%20held%20in%20Kartik%20on%20its%20full%20moon%20day%20and%20in%20Chait%20on%20Ram%20Navami%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20his%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20pictures%20following%20the%20tradition%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Panchayat%2C%20Ram%20is%20seen%20with%20Sita%20and%20his%20three%20brothers%20in%20a%20reassuring%20posture%20for%20everyone.%20His%20praises%20are%20also%20sung%20by%20the%20devotees%20who%20claim%20that%20despite%20conquering%20Lanka%20by%20killing%20Ravana%2C%20he%20did%20not%20capture%20it.%20Why%20would%20he%20grab%20it%20when%20he%20had%20abandoned%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20kingdom%20in%20Ayodhya%20too%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fkrishna-pratap-singh%5C%22%3EKrishna%20Pratap%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F261004%2Fayodhya-ram-mandir-trust-ramanandi-sampraday%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20Hindi%20original%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699447258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08173148%2FThe-Wire-70.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Faydhoya-temple-consecration-ramanandi-sect%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20medieval%20era%20tradition%20is%20known%20for%20coordination%20between%20different%20branches%20of%20Ra