ople%20that%20were%20earlier%20far%20from%20discernible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02103657%2FF3uRFgvW8AAhDHt.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02103657%2FF3uRFgvW8AAhDHt.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02103657%2FF3uRFgvW8AAhDHt-300x185.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671131%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40kharge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20urges%20especially%20brought%20out%20by%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20lay%20buried%20under%20bushels%20of%20communal%20propaganda%20fortified%20by%20the%20authoritarian%20agendas%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%2C%20which%20talks%20up%20the%20leader%20all%20the%20time.%20Train%20and%20plane%20passengers%20are%20also%20not%20spared.%20The%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20voters%20were%20won%20over%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20communal%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20leader%20shows%20the%20way%E2%80%9D%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECombined%20with%20the%20nationwide%20churning%20and%20mobilisation%2C%20the%20channelling%20of%20dissent%20and%20anti-regime%20sentiment%20produced%20by%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%20march%2C%20and%20the%20election%20of%20Kharge%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20political%20articulations%20and%20organisational%20clarity%20are%20widely%20credited%20for%20giving%20the%20Congress%20ballast%20as%20the%20party%20geared-up%20for%20state%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20can%20be%20said%20to%20be%20the%20high%20points%20of%20the%20year%202023%2C%20which%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20an%20extraordinary%20one%20for%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20point%20is%2C%20how%20is%20the%20year%20going%20to%20end%3F%20Channelling%20protests%20is%20all%20very%20well%2C%20but%20what%20will%20be%20the%20score-line%20on%20December%203%20when%20results%20become%20available%20for%20the%20three%20key%20Hindi-speaking%20heartland%20states%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20besides%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram%3F%20The%20social%20and%20cultural%20profile%20of%20North%20India%20can%20be%20said%20to%20be%20different%20from%20Karnataka%20where%20aggressive%20propagation%20of%20communal%20politics%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20himself%20failed%20to%20sway%20the%20voter%20last%20April-May.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-bypoll-ghosi-dhupguri-kerala-tripura%5C%22%3EINDIA%20Alliance%20Passes%20First%20By-Poll%20Test%20Well%2C%20But%20Needs%20to%20Sort%20Out%20Differences%20in%20Key%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20appears%20now%20to%20have%20put%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20camp%20of%20an%20adversary%20rather%20than%20an%20ally.%20He%20is%20unhappy%20for%20not%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseems-congress-doesnt-want-to-partner-with-us-akhilesh-yadav-4551422%5C%22%3ECongress%20backing%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20party%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20it%20has%20a%20marginal%20presence.%20The%20same%20is%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Aam%20Admi%20Party%20(AAP)%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20Both%20SP%20and%20AAP%20are%20fighting%20in%20many%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20of%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20%E2%80%93%20who%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20was%20instrumental%20in%20drumming%20up%20support%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20by%20bringing%20the%20regional%20parties%20in%20step%20(or%20so%20it%20seemed)%20with%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20too%20has%20candidates%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07214142%2FF-AjAdfbYAA6UOc.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22888%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07214142%2FF-AjAdfbYAA6UOc.jpeg%20888w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07214142%2FF-AjAdfbYAA6UOc-300x185.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22549%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENitish%20Kumar.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40NitishKumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20speaking%20in%20Patna%20recently%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fpatna-news%2Fat-cpi-rally-nitish-kumar-blames-congress-for-india-bloc-losing-steam-101698923029711.html%5C%22%3Eblamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Congress%20for%20paying%20insufficient%20attention%20to%20the%20organisational%20aspects%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20and%20focusing%20only%20on%20the%20five%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20five%20states%20where%20assembly%20elections%20are%20being%20held%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20a%20different%20category%20from%20the%20rest.%20Here%2C%20the%20BJP%20risks%20losing%20power%2C%20the%20same%20way%20as%20it%20did%20in%20Himachal%20and%20Karnataka.%20A%20gain%20for%20the%20Congress%20here%20can%20boost%20the%20opposition%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20for%20which%20preparations%20will%20commence%20shortly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20that%20SP%2C%20AAP%2C%20and%20to%20an%20extent%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20did%20not%20keep%20this%20in%20view.%20It%20is%20noteworthy%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20CPI%20and%20the%20CPI%20(M)%2C%20whose%20request%20for%20accommodation%20in%20the%20three%20North%20Indian%20states%2C%20were%20also%20not%20considered%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20have%20taken%20the%20situation%20stoically.%20Perhaps%20they%20have%20a%20different%20appreciation%20of%20the%20ideological%20stakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20and%20more%20broadly%20INDIA%20in%20its%20extant%20shape%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20%E2%80%93%20prepares%20the%20platform%20well%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%202024%20will%20depend%20in%20good%20measure%20on%20the%20result%20of%20the%20five%20state%20polls.%20If%20the%20opposition%20goes%20below%20par%2C%20it%20can%20cease%20to%20entertain%20any%20hopes%20for%20the%20parliament%20election%20while%20the%20BJP%20can%20still%20hope%20to%20live%20to%20fight%20another%20day%20if%20it%20slides%20toward%20defeat%20in%20the%20ongoing%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20extent%2C%20it%20can%20be%20asserted%20that%20INDIA%20%E2%80%93%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20%E2%80%93%20was%20not%20conceived%20only%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%2C%20although%20in%20his%20hubris%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%20display%20of%20deplorable%20diplomacy%20toward%20a%20presumed%20ally%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Congress%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath%20asserted%20while%20dismissing%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20with%20a%20wave%20of%20the%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20various%20points%20in%20the%20post-Rajiv%20Gandhi%20era%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20pondered%20its%20relationship%20with%20other%20opposition%20parties.%20The%20view%20at%20times%20has%20been%20to%20go%20it%20alone%20while%20at%20other%20times%20the%20value%20of%20teaming%20up%20with%20other%20parties%20has%20been%20considered.%20With%20the%20coming%20together%20of%20INDIA%2C%20it%20was%20felt%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20was%20persuaded%20that%20taking%20on%20the%20gargantuan%20BJP%20of%20the%20Modi%20era%20would%20call%20for%20the%20widest%20possible%20mobilisation%20of%20opposition%20forces.%20Indeed%2C%20this%20seemed%20the%20message%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20certain%20regional%20parties%20in%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20may%20be%20playing%20their%20games%2C%20and%20some%20may%20even%20be%20acting%20under%20remote%20guidance%20of%20the%20establishment%20since%20they%20may%20have%20been%20pressured%20by%20the%20coercive%20agencies%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20rather%20than%20any%20other%20party%20%E2%80%93%20that%20may%20be%20called%20upon%20to%20summon%20the%20wisest%20moves%20once%20the%20state%20polls%20are%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20the%20most%20at%20stake%20in%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20constitutional%20system%20that%20we%20have.%20It%20must%20not%20lose%20sight%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20while%20regional%20parties%20fight%20the%20BJP%20politically%20to%20guard%20their%20turf%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20for%20its%20survival%20and%20the%20survival%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20democracy%2C%20has%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20both%20politically%20and%20ideologically.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanand-k-sahay%5C%22%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20political%20commentator%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699443917000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18155503%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.20.10-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-parties-unease-congress-ideological-counter-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20blaming%20Congress%20for%20the%20alliance%20losing%20its%20initial%20steam%20or%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20taunting%20Congress%20for%20not%20supporting%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20examples%20of%20insecurity%20developed%20by%20regional%20parties%20of