thewire.in%2Fworld%2Fportugals-pm-antonio-costa-quits-amid-corruption-probe%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20Outsourced%20Critical%20Projects%20Worth%20Rs%20500%20Crore%20to%20Consultancies%20in%20Last%205%20Years%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08145721%2Fimage-1485.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20An%20investigation%20conducted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fin-5-years-16-ministries-gave-rs-500-crore-work-to-big-five-consultants-9018061%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20records%20obtained%20through%20the%20Right%20To%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%2C%20has%20revealed%20that%2016%20ministries%20and%20departments%20within%20the%20Union%20government%20have%20outsourced%20several%20critical%20assignments%20related%20to%20various%20aspects%20of%20governance%20to%20prominent%20multinational%20consultancy%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBetween%20April%202017%20and%20June%202022%2C%20the%20Big%20Four%20%E2%80%93%20Pricewater-houseCoopers%20(PwC)%2C%20Deloitte%20Touche%20Tohmatsu%20Limited%2C%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20Global%20Limited%20and%20KPMG%20International%20Limited%20%E2%80%93%20and%20US-based%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%2C%20bagged%20at%20least%20308%20consultancy%20assignments%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%20500%20crore%20from%20various%20government%20ministries%2C%20departments%20and%20organisations%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported%2C%20citing%20RTI%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2059%20ministries%20in%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20has%20named%20all%20the%2016%20departments%2F%20ministries%20and%20about%2050%20organisations%20under%20their%20administration%20that%20consulted%20any%20of%20the%20five%20global%20consultants.%20These%20are%20Petroleum%20and%20Natural%20Gas%3B%20Rural%20Development%3B%20Administrative%20Reforms%20and%20Public%20Grievances%3B%20Promotion%20of%20Industry%20and%20Internal%20Trade%3B%20Coal%3B%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%3B%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%3B%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Entrepreneurship%3B%20Defence%3B%20Civil%20Aviation%3B%20Public%20Enterprises%3B%20Non-conventional%20Energy%20Resources%3B%20Power%3B%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%3B%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%3B%20and%20Tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20these%20are%20just%20a%20few%20pixels%20of%20the%20big%20picture%20%E2%80%93%20RTI%20records%20made%20available%20to%3Cem%3E%20The%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20mainly%20from%20government%20wings%20in%20the%20petroleum%20and%20power%20sectors%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20RTI%20records%2C%20PwC%20was%20the%20biggest%20beneficiary%2C%20getting%20at%20least%2092%20contracts%20for%20over%20Rs%20156%20crore%20between%202017%20and%202022.%20Deloitte%20got%2059%20assignments%20worth%20over%20Rs%20130.13%20crore.%20However%2C%20the%20amounts%20involved%20in%20four%20of%20those%20contracts%20were%20not%20provided%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20E%26amp%3BY%20bagged%20as%20many%20as%2087%20contracts%20for%20Rs%2088.05%20crore%2C%20with%20amounts%20not%20provided%20for%20five%20of%20them%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKPMG%20got%2066%20contracts%20worth%20Rs%2068.46%20crore%2C%20without%20any%20data%20provided%20on%20amounts%20for%20five%20of%20them.%20And%20McKinsey%20got%20three%20contracts%20for%20Rs%2050.09%20crore%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petroleum%20sector%20received%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20assignments%2C%20valued%20at%20over%20Rs%20170%20crore%2C%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Petroleum%20and%20four%20of%20its%20PSUs%2C%20while%20nine%20organisations%20under%20the%20power%20ministry%20outsourced%20assignments%20worth%20Rs%20166.41%20crore%20to%20multinational%20consultancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20mentioned%20that%20state-owned%20Indian%20Oil%20Corporation%20declined%20to%20provide%20the%20data%20citing%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctrade%20secret%E2%80%9D%20clause%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20roster%20of%20ministries%20includes%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Tourism%20and%20NITI%20Aayog.%20Within%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Tourism%2C%20a%20minimum%20of%20Rs%2018%20crore%20worth%20of%20work%20was%20awarded%20to%20E%26amp%3BY%20alone%20as%20part%20of%20its%20Swadesh%20Darshan%20initiative.%20Meanwhile%2C%20NITI%20Aayog%20outsourced%20seven%20assignments%2C%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2017.43%20crore%2C%20between%202019%20and%202021%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cevaluation%20of%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%202015%2C%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fservices%2Fconsultancy-%2F-audit%2Fconsultancies-benefiting-from-modi-governments-push-on-projects-like-digital-india-swachh-bharat%2Farticleshow%2F48168768.cms%5C%22%3Enews%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20highlighted%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20practice%20of%20engaging%20consultants%20for%20initiatives%20like%20Make%20in%20India%2C%20Digital%20India%2C%20smart%20cities%2C%20Swachh%20Bharat%2C%20and%20skill%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202015%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fservices%2Fconsultancy-%2F-audit%2Fconsultancies-benefiting-from-modi-governments-push-on-projects-like-digital-india-swachh-bharat%2Farticleshow%2F48168768.cms%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20quoting%20senior%20consultants%2C%20that%20these%20consultancies%20were%20paid%20around%20Rs%20500%20crore%20in%20fees%20in%20the%20year%20ended%20March.%20And%20they%20said%20that%20in%20a%20year%E2%80%99s%20ti