The%20Tide%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Epremiered%20in%20the%20World%20Cinema%20Documentary%20Competition%20at%20Sundance%20and%20received%20a%20special%20jury%20prize%2C%20and%20has%20since%20won%20eight%20awards%20before%20MAMI%2C%20including%20UN%20Perception%20Change%20Award%20at%20Visions%20du%20R%C3%A9el%202023%2C%20Grand%20Jury%20Prize%20in%20the%20Documentary%20Competition%20at%20Seattle%20IFF%202023%2C%20Sustainable%20Future%20Award%20at%20Sydney%20IFF%202023%20and%20Best%20Feature%20Award%20at%20Ice%20Docs%202023%2C%20Best%20Documentary%20at%20International%20South%20Asian%20Film%20Festival%20Canada%20and%20the%20Asian%20Pacific%20Screen%20Award%20(APSA)%20in%20best%20documentary%20category.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20quite%20an%20achievement%2C%20since%20this%20is%20just%20her%20second%20film%3B%20the%20first%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Ballad%20Of%20Maladies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20about%20music%20as%20a%20means%20of%20protest%20by%20the%20youth%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20made%20in%202016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGanesh%20Nakhawa%20belongs%20to%20a%20relatively%20prosperous%20family%2C%20he%20studied%20in%20Scotland%2C%20lives%20in%20a%20large%20apartment%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20has%20a%20fleet%20of%20modern%20fishing%20boats%20and%20drives%20a%20car%20with%20his%20Instagram%20handle%C2%A0%E2%80%98Last%20fisherman%20of%20Bombay%E2%80%99%C2%A0painted%20on%20the%20side.%20Rakesh%20Koli%2C%20also%20a%20fisherman%2C%20lives%20in%20a%20toilet-less%20shanty%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20mother%20and%20ailing%20infant.%20His%20family%20believes%20in%20traditional%20methods%20of%20fishing%20%E2%80%93%20in%20small%20boats%20in%20shallow%20waters.%20He%20is%20strongly%20against%20deep%20sea%20fishing%2C%20even%20if%20the%20nets%20bring%20in%20more%20garbage%20and%20dead%20fish%20than%20catch%20that%20can%20be%20sold%20for%20good%20prices.%20His%20new-born%20has%20a%20heart%20problem%20that%20eats%20up%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20meagre%20finances%2C%20and%20at%20some%20point%2C%20Rakesh%20has%20to%20sell%20his%20boat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGanesh%20too%20has%20severe%20money%20troubles%20because%20he%20has%20mortgaged%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20jewellery%2C%20taken%20huge%20loans%20to%20modernise%20his%20boats%2C%20and%20also%20used%20the%20legally%20forbidden%20LED%20method%20(using%20strong%20lights%20underwater%20to%20attract%20more%20fish)%20to%20get%20a%20large%20haul%2C%20but%20when%20the%20oceans%20have%20been%20depleted%2C%20there%20is%20cause%20for%20worry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20their%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edifferent%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epoints%20of%20view%20and%20lifestyles%2C%20Ganesh%20and%20Rakesh%20meet%20often%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20to%20disagree%3B%20Ganesh%20is%20there%20for%20his%20buddy%20when%20the%20child%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20hospital%3B%20Rakesh%20and%20his%20family%20turn%20up%20for%20the%20birthday%20party%20of%20Ganesh%E2%80%99s%20grandfather.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20documentary%2C%20where%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20script%20scenes%20or%20predict%20which%20way%20an%20interaction%20will%20go%2C%20Sarvnik%20Kaur%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(also%20a%20co-producer)%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emanages%20to%20build%20up%20emotional%20conflict%20and%20drama%20between%20the%20two%20men%20and%20also%20takes%20in%20the%20larger%20picture%20of%20a%20polluted%2C%20endangered%20ecosystem%20that%20threatens%20to%20destroy%20the%20livelihood%20of%20the%20fisherfolk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20it%20might%20become%20untenable%20for%20Kolis%20to%20survive%20in%20their%20ancestral%20profession.%20As%20the%20younger%20generation%20looks%20for%20other%20jobs%2C%20it%20also%20signals%20the%20end%20of%20a%20rich%20culture%20of%20stories%2C%20rituals%2C%20songs%2C%20dances%2C%20language%20and%20community%20bonds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fbahadur-the-brave-shows-how-for-nepalese-migrant-workers-the-lockdown-was-even-more-difficult%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dfilm-%2CBahadur%2520the%2520Brave%2520Shows%2520How%2520For%2520Nepalese%2520Migrant%2520Workers%252C%2520the%2Csensitive%2520look%2520at%2520their%2520travails.%5C%22%3EBahadur%20the%20Brave%20Shows%20How%20For%20Nepalese%20Migrant%20Workers%2C%20the%20Lockdown%20was%20Even%20More%20Difficult%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERakesh%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20who%20opens%20the%20film%20giving%20the%20screaming%20child%20a%20massage%2C%20believes%20in%20the%20benevolence%20of%20the%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cocean%20goddess%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20traditional%20methods%20of%20fishing%3B%20but%20when%20Rakesh%E2%80%99s%20boat%20is%20sold%20and%20she%20is%20reduced%20to%20helpless%20tears%2C%20she%20still%20blesses%20the%20buyer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShot%20beautifully%20by%20Ashok%20Meena%2C%20there%20are%20stunning%20images%20of%20the%20sunrises%20and%20sunsets%2C%20the%20shimmering%20sea%20and%20underwater%20shots%20of%20marine%20life%2C%20fascinating%20sequences%20of%20the%20net-casting%20and%20fishing%20operation%2C%20but%20Kaur%20has%20also%20chosen%20her%20protagonists%20well%20%E2%80%93%20they%20have%20expressive%20faces%20and%20well-articulated%20opinions.%20There%20is%20an%20air%20of%20doom%20but%20also%20hope%20as%20they%20navigate%20their%20boats%2C%20in%20the%20search%20of%20that%20one%20massive%20catch%20that%20will%20rescue%20them%20from%20sinking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResidents%20of%20Mumbai%20must%20have%20noticed%20that%20over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20Koli%20women%20%E2%80%93%20dressed%20in%20distinctive%20outfits%2C%20a%20sari%20worn%20in%20a%20peculiar%20style%20with%20a%20white%20dupatta%20and%20heavy%20gold%20jewellery%20%E2%80%93%20who%20used%20to%20come%20around%20with%20baskets%20of%20fish%2C%20have%20stopped%20their%20morning%20rounds.%20Some%20Koli%20settlements%2C%20particularly%20in%20Versova%20in%20north%20Mumbai%2C%20have%20made%20way%20for%20apartment%20blocks%20and%20the%20smell%20of%20drying%20fish%20that%20used%20to%20permeate%20the%20air%20is%20missing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20monsoon%2C%20at%20high%20tide%2C%20the%20sea%20throws%20back%20the%20mounds%20of%20trash%20thrown%20into%20it%20that%20have%20been%20causing%20destruction%20of%20marine%20life.%20Development%20projects%20on%20the%20coast%20have%20also%20cut%20into%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20catch%2C%20and%20fishermen%20are%20forced%20to%20take%20their%20boats%20deeper%20into%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaur%E2%80%99s%20film%20has%20caught%20the%20Koli%20community%20%E2%80%93%20the%20original%20inhabitants%20of%20the%20city%2C%20who%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20fishing%20for%20generations%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20change.%20But%20it%20may%20already%20be%20too%20late%20to%20reverse%20the%20damage%20caused%20by%20greed%20(overfishing)%20and%20apathy%20(pollution%20of%20sea%20water).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGanesh%20and%20Rakesh%20are%20two%20tiny%20specks%20in%20the%20vast%20expanse%20of%20the%20ocean%2C%20and%20saving%20the%20environment%20is%20beyond%20them.%20All%20they%20can%20do%20is%20tell%20their%20story%2C%20and%20luckily%20Sarvnik%20Kaur%20has%20taken%20it%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699433402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08135713%2F1600px-Fish_a_lot_of_fish_2152054969.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fa-new-documentary-captures-the-bleak-future-of-mumbais-original-inhabitants-the-koli-community%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarvnik%20Kaur%E2%80%99s%20evocative%20film%20on%20the%20fishing%20community%20has%20already%20won%20awards%20in%20festivals%20all%20over%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fa-new-documentary-captures-the-bleak-future-of-mumbais-original-inhabitants-the-koli-community%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Visva-Bharati%2C%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%2C%20and%20I%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25143825%2FIMG_3324.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fvisva-bharati-vc-bidyut-chakraborty-controversial-legacy%5C%22%3EBidyut%20Chakrabarty%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fvisva-bharati-vc-bidyut-chakraborty-controversial-legacy%5C%22%3Etenure%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Vice-Chancellor%20of%20Vishva-Bharati%20University%2C%20which%20ends%20today%2C%20has%20been%20a%20very%20turbulent%20one.%20He%20is%20a%20political%20scientist%20who%20has%20authored%20a%20number%20of%20books%20including%20one%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Socio-Political%20Ideas%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%3A%20Liberal%20Constitutionalism%20in%20a%20Creative%20Mould%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0published%20in%202018%20by%20Routledge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20book%E2%80%99s%20preface%2C%20Chakrabarty%20writes%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20relatively%20less-known%20fact%20that%20without%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%3B%E2%80%99s%20personal%20intervention%2C%20Ambedkar%20may%20not%20have%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20chairman%20%5Bof%20the%20drafting%20committee%20of%20the%20Constitution%5D%20since%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20had%20already%20zeroed%20in%20on%20Ivor%20Jennings%2C%20an%20eminent%20Constitutional%20lawyer%20and%20an%20equally%20renowned%20Cambridge%20academic%2C%20for%20the%20responsibility%E2%80%A6%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%A6was%20keen%20that%20Ambedkar%20should%20have%20been%20in%20the%20%5BConstituent%5D%20Assembly%3B%20it%20was%20made%20possible%20because%20Jogendra%20Nath%20Bengal%2C%20a%20prominent%20Dalit%20leader%20from%20Bengal%2C%20sacrificed%20his%20seat%20for%20Ambedkar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20obviously%20a%20typographical%20error%20in%20this%20paragraph.%20The%20reference%20should%20be%20to%20Jogendra%20Nath%20Mandal%20and%20not%20%E2%80%98Jogendra%20Nath%20Bengal%E2%80%99.%20But%20there%20are%20far%20more%20serious%20issues%20here%20that%20reflect%20both%20shoddy%20and%20mischievous%20right-wing%20writings%20that%20masquerade%20as%20scholarship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20while%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20was%20certainly%20very%20keen%20that%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20be%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20Ramachandra%20Guha%20in%20his%202018%20magnum%20opus%20%3Cem%3EGandhi%3A%20The%20Years%20That%20Changed%20the%20World%2C%201914-1948%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0has%20revealed%20the%20role%20that%20Rajkumari%20Amrit%20Kaur%20and%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20played%2C%20with%20the%20full%20backing%20of%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20ensuring%20that%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20became%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20And%20Ashok%20Gopal%20in%20his%202023%20biography%20%3Cem%3EA%20Part%20Apart%3A%20The%20Life%20and%20Thought%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0has%20described%20why%20and%20how%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20was%20keen%20on%20becoming%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20in%20spite%20of%20his%20long%20opposition%20to%20both%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20true%20to%20say%20that%20Jogendra%20Nath%20Mandal%20masterminded%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20election%20to%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20from%20then-undivided%20Bengal.%20The%20definitive%202018%20biography%20of%20Mandal%20by%20Dwaipayan%20Sen%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Decline%20of%20the%20Caste%20Question%3A%20Jogendranath%20Mandal%20and%20the%20Defeat%20of%20Dalit%20Politics%20in%20Bengal%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20describes%20Mandal%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20role%20in%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20great%20detail.%20But%20contrary%20to%20what%20Chakrabarty%20claims%2C%20Mandal%20did%20not%20give%20up%20his%20seat%20for%20Dr.%20Ambedkar.%20%3Cem%3EB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eoth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20elected.%20Mandal%20later%20became%20the%20first%20law%20minister%20of%20Pakistan%20before%20returning%20to%20India%20in%201950.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%20and%20this%20is%20far%20more%20insidious%2C%20Chakrabarty%20provides%20no%20evidence%20whatsoever%20for%20his%20extraordinary%20claim%20that%20Nehru%20wanted%20Ivor%20Jennings%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20Drafting%20Committee.%20This%20allegation%C2%A0%20of%20Chakrabarty%E2%80%99s%20has%20most%20recently%20been%20repeated%20in%20a%20book%20on%20the%20constitution%20by%20Arghya%20Sengupta%20who%20simply%20writes%20that%20his%20source%20is%20Chakrabarty%20who%20himself%2C%20it%20should%20be%20reiterated%2C%20has%20given%20no%20source%20whatsoever%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20This%20is%20how%20falsehoods%20get%20repeated%20and%20gain%20currency%20of%20their%20own.%20Jennings%2C%20incidentally%20between%201946%20and%201948%2C%20did%20draft%20a%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20that%20of%20what%20was%20then%20called%20Ceylon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgtXTk8Zs-ns%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Does%20India%20Have%20a%20Colonial%20Consitituion%20Or%20is%20That%20a%20Mistaken%20View%3F%20%7C%20Karan%20Thapar%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20most%20intrigued%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20Chakrabarty%20on%20October%2023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20wrote%20to%20him%20thus%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20to%20you%20after%20reading%20Arghya%20Sengupta%E2%80%99s%20new%20book%20on%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20He%20quotes%20you%20as%20having%20written%20that%20Nehru%20opposed%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20as%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Drafting%20Committee%20and%20wanted%20Ivor%20Jennings%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20then%20looked%20up%20your%20book%20which%20Arghya%20has%20drawn%20from%20but%20could%20not%20find%20the%20source%20that%20you%20have%20used%20for%20your%20definitive%20statement.%20I%20also%20relooked%20at%20Shiva%20Rao%20and%20Austin%20as%20also%20two%20recent%20bios%20of%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20and%20of%20Jennings%20too.%20I%20also%20went%20through%20the%20CA%20papers%20of%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20and%20a%20few%20other%20materials%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20could%20not%20find%20any%20confirmation%20%E2%80%93%20even%20remote%20%E2%80%93%20of%20what%20you%20have%20written.%20But%20since%20you%20are%20a%20distinguished%20academic%20I%20am%20sure%20you%20would%20have%20had%20your%20own%20source%20for%20the%20statement%20in%20your%20book.%20More%20as%20a%20semi-academic%20myself%20I%20would%20very%20much%20like%20to%20get%20educated%20and%20enlightened%20on%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20your%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20regards%20and%20congratulations%20for%20the%20UNESCO%20heritage%20tag%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20he%20replied%20to%20me%20on%20WhatsApp%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20you%20are%20a%20sensible%20person%20and%20above%20petty%20politics.%20Your%20irresponsible%20comment%20is%20explicable%20because%20you%20are%20oath-bound%20to%20what%20sycophants%20like%20you%20consider%20the%20first%20family%20of%20India.%20I%20understand%20your%20predicament%20because%20given%20your%20servility%20to%20specific%20individuals%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20lose%20an%20opportunity%20to%20show%20your%20loyalty%20to%20them%20because%20your%20irrational%20statement%20is%20also%20meant%20to%20make%20the%20fools%20believe%20that%20a%20futile%20conglomeration%20INDIA%20is%20realistic%20coalition.%20Cracks%20have%20already%20been%20visible!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20flabbergasted%20to%20say%20the%20least%20to%20receive%20this%20response%20to%20what%20I%20thought%20was%20a%20perfectly%20straight-forward%20request.%20I%20immediately%20replied%20on%20the%20same%20medium%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20does%20not%20answer%20my%20question%20Professor.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20know%20your%20source.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20reply%20was%2C%20I%20must%20admit%2C%20quick%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPlease%20do%20come%20down%20to%20Viswa-Bharati%20and%20then%20the%20source%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20a%20sycophant%20like%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20could%20not%20resist%20messaging%20back%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSure%20will%20do%20so%20but%20abuses%20ill-become%20an%20academic%20like%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChakrabarty%20was%20not%20done%20however%20and%20replied%20instantly%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20an%20abuse%20but%20a%20realistic%20description%20of%20individuals%20like%20you%20who%20thrive%20by%20being%20sycophant%20without%20assessing%20whether%20what%20you%20stated%20in%20your%20email%20is%20also%20an%20abuse.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wanted%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20exchange%20and%20signed%20off%20saying%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COh%20well.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20reveal%20the%20source%20of%20your%20definitive%20statement%20it%20is%20fine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20Professor%20was%20not%20done%20and%20had%20the%20last%20word%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20you%20are%20good%20at%20distorting%20truth.%20What%20I%20stated%20in%20my%20message%20is%20to%20get%20the%20input%20please%20come%20down%20to%20Viswa-Bharati%20if%20you%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20face%20the%20bitter%20truth%20where%20you%20will%20not%20be%20saved%20by%20your%C2%A0%20God%20father%20or%20God%20mother!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20to%20make%20of%20this%20somewhat%20bizarre%20conversation%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrankly%2C%20Chakrabarty%20wants%20to%20impart%20intellectual%20respectability%20to%20the%20appropriation%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20by%20the%20right-wing.%20If%2C%20in%20the%20process%2C%20more%20mud%20can%20be%20flung%20at%20Nehru%20without%20rhyme%20or%20reason%20all%20the%20more%20better.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20100%25%20sure%20that%20he%20has%20no%20clinching%20archival%20proof%20for%20his%20statement%20on%20Nehru%20and%20Jennings%20%E2%80%93%20a%20statement%20that%20is%20blatantly%20and%20patently%20mischievous.%20There%20is%20every%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20what%20Granville%20Austin%20termed%20the%20guiding%20%E2%80%98oligarchy%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20%E2%80%93%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20and%20Maulana%20Azad%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20had%20between%20themselves%20decided%20on%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20Drafting%20Committee.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2029%2C%201947%2C%20members%20of%20the%20drafting%20committee%20chose%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20from%20among%20themselves%20to%C2%A0%20be%20the%20chairman.%20His%20obvious%20distinction%20had%20made%20him%20a%20natural%20candidate%20for%20chairmanship.%20Besides%2C%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20was%20also%20Union%20law%20minister.%20Nehru%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20written%20to%20Patel%20on%20July%2030%2C%201947%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20spoken%20to%20Ambedkar%20and%20he%20has%20agreed%20%5Bto%20be%20Union%20law%20minister%5D.%20He%20said%20Law%20would%20not%20give%20him%20enough%20work.%20I%20told%20him%20he%20need%20not%20worry%20about%20that.%20There%20will%20be%20plenty%20of%20work%20of%20many%20kinds%20to%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20would%20normally%20not%20have%20bothered%20too%20much%20but%20discovered%20that%20Ivor%20Jennings%E2%80%99%20Wikipedia%20entry%20has%20a%20reference%20to%20Chakrabarty%E2%80%99s%20claim.%20This%20is%20how%20lies%20are%20spread%20in%20the%20digital%20world%20and%20need%20to%20be%20exposed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Congress%20MP%2C%20is%20a%20part-time%20author.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699433260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25143825%2FIMG_3324.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvisva-bharati-the-vice-chancellor-and-i%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bidyut%20Chakrabarty%20wants%20to%20impart%20intellectual%20respectability%20to%20the%20appropriation%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20by%20the%20right-wing.%20But%20the%20facts%20remain%20unsubstantiated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvisva-bharati-the-vice-chancellor-and-i%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2233%25%20Indian%20Women%20Can't%20Access%20Contraception%3A%20Outrage%20At%20This%2C%20Not%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20Words%20on%20Withdrawal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02190722%2FNitish-Kumar.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20constitutes%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20dignity%20of%20a%20woman%3F%20Ravaging%20her%20malnourished%20body%20to%20cause%20repeated%20pregnancies%20or%20talking%20about%20ways%20that%20she%20can%20avoid%20such%20a%20fate%20even%20when%20society%20and%20the%20government%20have%20failed%20in%20their%20duty%20to%20help%20her%20access%20contraception%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20questions%20are%20important%20when%20large%20sections%20of%20even%20the%20%E2%80%9Cliberated%E2%80%9D%20are%20outraged%20over%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20graphic%20description%20of%20withdrawal%20as%20one%20of%20the%20means%20that%20an%20educated%20woman%20can%20make%20her%20husband%20practice%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20unwanted%20pregnancies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiggling%20and%20blushing%20MLAs%20all%20around%20him%20%E2%80%93%20Kumar%20himself%20succumbs%20to%20a%20fit%20of%20laughter%20for%20a%20while%20%E2%80%93%20contribute%20to%20the%20trivialisation%20of%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20as%20much%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20bane%20as%20the%20reluctance%20to%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20behind%20it%20without%20shame%20and%20manufactured%20outrage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESex%20is%20a%20taboo%20word%20in%20a%20country%20that%20produces%2025%20million%20children%20every%20year.%20Safe%20sex%20is%20anathema.%20Talking%20about%20it%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20sacrilege!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%205%20(data%20from%202019-20)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FIndia.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esays%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20only%2066.7%25%20Indian%20women%20have%20access%20to%20any%20method%20of%20contraception%20and%20just%2056.5%25%20have%20access%20to%20a%20modern%20method.%20(A%20modern%20method%20refers%20to%20sterilisation%2C%20contraceptive%20pills%2C%20condoms%2C%20intrauterine%20devices%20or%20injectable%20contraceptives.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FBihar.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBihar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20numbers%20are%2055.8%25%20for%20any%20method%20and%2044.4%25%20for%20any%20modern%20method.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20description%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20of%20withdrawal%2C%20a%20method%20where%20the%20man%20retracts%20before%20ejaculation.%20It%20is%20an%20accepted%20mode%20of%20contraception%20in%20any%20basic%20physiology%20textbook%2C%20albeit%20an%20unreliable%20one.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20total%20fertility%20rate%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20the%20average%20number%20of%20children%20that%20a%20woman%20would%20give%20birth%20to%20during%20her%20life%20time%20%E2%80%93%20stands%20according%20to%20NFHS%205%20at%203%20in%20Bihar%20while%20the%20national%20average%20stands%20at%202.2%20which%20is%20just%20a%20notch%20above%20the%20replacement%20fertility%20rate%20of%202.1.%20Replacement%20fertility%20refers%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20population%20stops%20actually%20growing%20as%20death%20and%20birth%20rates%20reach%20a%20balance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20times%20immemorial%20governments%20in%20India%20have%20made%20family%20planning%20%E2%80%93%20euphemism%20for%20reducing%20births%20%E2%80%93%20their%20business.%20Yet%20if%2033%25%20Indian%20women%20and%2045%25%20Bihari%20women%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20any%20method%20of%20contraception%20that%20should%20be%20the%20cause%20for%20real%20outrage%20for%20all.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20squeamishness%20to%20talk%20about%20sex%20and%20the%20political%20backlash%20that%20anything%20akin%20to%20sex%20education%20invariably%20generates%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20Indian%20men%20get%20their%20sex%20education%20from%20pornography%20materials%20and%20women%20largely%20get%20it%20from%20life%2C%20learning%20the%20hard%20way%20about%20what%20can%20cause%20a%20pregnancy%20often%20ending%20up%20as%20unwitting%20victims%20of%20a%20system%20that%20is%20quick%20to%20punish%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnmet%20contraceptive%20needs%20lead%20to%20illegal%20abortions%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20need%20for%20contraception%20and%20sex%20education%20go%20beyond%20the%20need%20of%20limiting%20family%20size%20which%20in%20itself%20is%20a%20multilayered%20proposition%20with%20implications%20on%20health%2C%20education%2C%20economic%20status%20etc%20of%20a%20family.%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20life%20and%20death.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20seminal%20book%20%3Cem%3EPutting%20Women%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%20based%20on%20her%20own%20gynaecology%20practice%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20Bang%20gives%20innumerable%20examples%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%93%20some%20of%20them%20as%20young%20as%2013%20%E2%80%93%20getting%20pregnant%20within%20weeks%20of%20menarche%2C%20sometimes%20not%20realising%20that%20they%20are%20pregnant%20till%20its%20too%20late%20to%20abort%20and%20then%20victimised%20by%20the%20tribal%20society%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cmistakes%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20telling%20statement%20on%20what%20lack%20of%20sex%20education%20does%20to%20young%20people%2C%20Dr%20Bang%20recounts%20the%20tale%20of%20a%20young%20boy%20who%20wrote%20her%20a%20letter%20addressing%20her%20as%20%E2%80%9Cauntie%E2%80%9D%20to%20talk%20about%20his%20own%20adolescent%20sexual%20insecurities%20and%20of%20a%20married%20couple%20who%20arrived%20at%20her%20clinic%20unsure%20about%20what%20constitutes%20the%20sexual%20act.%20She%20recounts%20countless%20cases%20in%20great%20detail%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20who%20had%20landed%20up%20at%20her%20clinic%20demanding%20an%20abortion%20past%20the%20legal%20timelines%20and%20then%20ending%20up%20either%20with%20an%20illegal%20abortion%20or%20worse%20still%20delivering%20an%20unwanted%20baby%20that%20is%20buried%20alive%20as%20per%20local%20practices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Population%20Fund%20(UNFPA)%E2%80%99s%20State%20of%20the%20World%20Population%20Report%202022.%20Between%202007-2011%2C%2067%25%20of%20abortions%20in%20India%20were%20classified%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findia-unintended-pregnancy-abortion-7845655%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunsafe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Many%20of%20them%20happen%20first%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20contraceptive%20access%20and%20awareness%2C%20then%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20safe%20(and%20non%20judgemental)%20abortion%20facilities.%20Every%20day%20an%20estimated%208%20women%20die%20in%20India%20because%20of%20unsafe%20abortions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Bang%20is%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%C2%A0%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsearchforhealth.ngo%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESociety%20for%20Education%2C%20Action%20and%20Research%20in%20Community%20Health%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(SEARCH)%20which%20runs%20a%20100%20bed%20hospital%20in%20Gadchiroli%20and%20has%20been%20a%20pioneer%20in%20many%20public%20health%20initiatives%20that%20have%20over%20the%20years%20been%20integrated%20into%20national%20programmes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20women%20are%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20contraception%20and%20often%20at%20a%20loss%20about%20how%20to%20access%20it%20was%20evident%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Flifestyle%2Fhealth%2Finjectable-contraceptives-at-mewat-women-get-shot-of-empowerment-5417216%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMewat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20categorised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20backward%20districts%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20immediately%20after%20the%20inclusion%20of%20injectable%20contraceptives%20in%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission%20basket%20saw%20women%20turning%20up%20at%20the%20clinics%20for%20a%20shot%2C%20often%20without%20telling%20their%20families.%20The%20women%20told%20me%20they%20wanted%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20cycle%20of%20annual%20pregnancies%20in%20which%20many%20of%20them%20were%20caught%20and%20as%20the%20local%20health%20workers%20talked%20to%20them%20about%20options%2C%20that%20of%20getting%20a%20shot%20that%20would%20prevent%20pregnancies%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20was%20a%20godsend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20the%20assembly%20gives%20women%20access%20to%20one%20more%20method%20of%20contraception%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20rudimentary%20and%20primitive%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20a%20few%20laughs.%20The%20outrage%20can%20be%20reserved%20for%20more%20deserving%20causes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAbantika%20Ghosh%20is%20a%20former%20journalist%20and%20author.%20She%20currently%20works%20with%20Chase%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699432843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02190722%2FNitish-Kumar.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnitish-kumar-withdrawal-contraception-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20trivialisation%20of%20this%20issue%20has%20as%20much%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20bane%20as%20the%20reluctance%20to%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20behind%20it%20without%20shame%20and%20manufactured%20outrage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnitish-kumar-withdrawal-contraception-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Ethics%20Panel's%20Next%20Meeting%20Date%20Ensures%20Another%20Non-BJP%20Member%20Can't%20Attend'%3A%20Mahua%20Moitra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F04145325%2F2022_2img03_Feb_2022_PTI02_03_2022_000159B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Two%20days%20before%20the%20parliament%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3Es%20ethics%20committee%20is%20to%20meet%20to%20consider%20adopting%20its%20%E2%80%98draft%20report%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20against%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20she%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20when%20it%20meets%20this%20November%209%2C%20its%20composition%20will%20be%20tilted%20even%20further%20towards%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20an%20allegation%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20that%20Moitra%20accepted%20bribes%20from%20Dubai-based%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%2C%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20forwarded%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20ethics%20committee.%20This%20also%20meant%20he%20had%20to%20constitute%20the%20committee%20as%20it%20was%20not%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBirla%20formed%20a%2015-member%20committee%2C%20naming%20seven%20members%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20one%20from%20the%20pro-BJP%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20three%20from%20Congress%20and%20one%20each%20from%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Yuvajana%20Sramika%20Rythu%20Congress%20Party%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United).%20The%20committee%20was%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20has%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20committee%20constituted%20to%20probe%20the%20complaint%20filed%20against%20the%20opposition%20MP%20who%20has%20not%20only%20been%20a%20vociferous%20critic%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20but%20had%20also%20openly%20accused%20the%20complainant%20Dubey%20some%20time%20ago%20of%20submitting%20what%20she%20claimed%20was%20a%20fake%20degree%20along%20with%20his%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Moitra%20has%20told%20reporters%20that%20Dubey%20filed%20the%20complaint%20against%20her%20because%20she%20inquired%20about%20his%20degree.%20The%20BJP%20MP%20has%20filed%20the%20complaint%20along%20with%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20whom%20Moitra%20has%20termed%20as%20her%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3Ejilted%20ex%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20says%20the%20reason%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20targeting%20her%20is%20because%20she%20has%20been%20asking%20the%20Modi%20government%20several%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%20its%20alleged%20favouritism%20towards%20the%20Gujarati%20business%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20says%20Sonkar%20has%20picked%20November%209%20as%20the%20date%20for%20the%20ethics%20committee%20meeting%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20member%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20a%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Telangana%2C%20is%20unable%20to%20attend%20it.%20The%20MP%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20is%20contesting%20the%20forthcoming%20Telangana%20assembly%20elections%20and%20has%20to%20be%20in%20his%20constituency%20to%20file%20his%20nomination%20papers%20on%20November%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20meeting%20of%20the%20ethics%20committee%2C%20five%20Opposition%20MPs%20including%20Reddy%20had%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20chairperson%20asking%20Moitra%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3Eindecent%20questions%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Moitra%20too%20had%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%20at%20the%20line%20of%20questioning%20which%20she%20said%20was%20equal%20to%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3EVastraharan%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ein%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20had%20put%20in%20her%20request%20to%20the%20chairperson%20to%20cross-examine%20both%20Dehadrai%20and%20Hiranandani%20who%20had%20submitted%20a%20%3Cem%3Esuo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emotu%3C%2Fem%3E%20affidavit%20to%20the%20committee%20claiming%20he%20had%20accessed%20her%20official%20email%20account%20to%20post%20parliamentary%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmahua-moitra-ramesh-bidhuri-very-different-parliament-committee%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Very%20Different%20Approach%20for%20BJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99%3A%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Writes%20to%20Parliament%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20social%20media%2C%20Moitra%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20though%20the%20chairperson%20had%20announced%20that%20the%20November%209%20meeting%20would%20consider%20adopting%20a%20draft%20report%20on%20the%20complaint%2C%20no%20such%20report%20has%20been%20circulated%20among%20the%20members%20yet.%20She%20also%20added%2C%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3EBJP%20calling%20allies%20to%20ensure%20attendance%20to%20adopt%20(the%20draft%20report)%20via%20majority.%20Chartered%20flight%20to%20fly%20in%20MP(Madhya%20Pradesh)%20state%20president%20(V.%20D.%20Sharma).%20How%20scared%20Adani%20%26amp%3B%20Modi%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDubey%20also%20took%20to%20X%20to%20claim%20that%20it%20was%20her%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Eguilty%20conscience%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20led%20her%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20panel%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENews%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmahua-moitra-cash-for-query-case-ethics-panel-likely-to-recommend-strict-actions-including-disqualification-of-tmc-mp-11699233232862.html%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20said%20th