%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposal%20garnered%20unanimous%20support%20from%20all%20councillors%2C%20and%20it%20will%20now%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20government%20for%20their%20consideration.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20that%20the%20government%20will%20respond%20positively%20to%20our%20request.%20The%20renaming%20of%20Aligarh%20to%20Harigarh%20has%20been%20a%20long%20standing%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20mayor%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagra%2Faligarh-may-soon-be-renamed-harigarh-resolution-passed-in-civic-body-meeting%2Farticleshow%2F105052570.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20proposal%20to%20rename%20Aligarh%20was%20cleared%20by%20a%20zila%20panchayat%20meeting%20in%202021%20as%20well%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Fnational%2Fproposal-to-change-the-name-of-aligarh-to-harigarh-passed%5C%22%3Eno%20developments%20took%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20was%20sent%20to%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Aligarh%20civic%20body%20is%20now%20reviving%20the%20issue.%20The%20district%20councils%20of%20Aligarh%20and%20Mainpuri%20had%20passed%20similar%20resolutions%20in%202022%20as%20well%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagra%2Faligarh-may-soon-be-renamed-harigarh-resolution-passed-in-civic-body-meeting%2Farticleshow%2F105052570.cms%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%20The%20Mainpuri%20district%20council%20had%20sought%20to%20rename%20Mainpuri%20to%20Mayan%20Nagar.%20According%20to%20the%20Mainpuri%20district%20council%20president%2C%20the%20district%20was%20originally%20founded%20by%20the%20sage%20Mayan%20hence%20it%20should%20be%20renamed%20as%20Mayan%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20renaming%20of%20these%20two%20districts%20is%20set%20to