was%20renamed%20as%20Pandit%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyaya%20junction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffrom-aligarh-to-harigarh-uttar-pradesh-continues-its-name-changing-spree%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Four%20Persons%2C%20Including%20Kin%20of%20a%20Soldier%2C%20Abducted%20by%20Armed%20Men%20from%20Kangchup%20Chingkhong%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15123624%2FF6AFowSaIAEUMh9.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFive%20members%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20were%20abducted%20from%20the%20border%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zomi-dominated%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Meitei-dominated%20Imphal%20West%20district%20in%20Manipur%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%208%20morning.%20Of%20the%20five%20abducted%2C%20four%20of%20them%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20family%20members%20of%20a%20soldier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecurity%20forces%20rescued%20one%20of%20the%20kidnapped%20persons%20after%20the%20exchange%20of%20fire%20with%20armed%20men%2C%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20abduction.%20At%20least%20nine%20people%2C%20including%20two%20policemen%2C%20have%20sustained%20injuries.%20Manglun%20Haokip%20(65)%2C%20who%20was%20rescued%20from%20kidnappers%20and%20sustained%20grievous%20injuries%2C%20has%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20military%20hospital%20in%20Leimakhong.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20clue%20of%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20others%20until%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20according%20to%20police.%20The%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%20organisations%20said%20the%20missing%20people%20include%20two%20women%20%E2%80%93%20aged%2060%20and%2055%20%E2%80%93%20and%20two%20men%2C%20aged%2040%20and%2025.%20They%20were%20abducted%20by%20armed%20men%20around%208%3A45%20am%2C%20close%20to%20Kangchup%20Chinkhong%2C%20which%20is%20at%20the%20border%20of%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Imphal%20West%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%2007.11.2023%2C%20at%20Kangchup%20Chingkhong%2C%20a%20Bolero%20carrying%20five%20individuals(2%20women%20and%203%20men)%20en-route%20from%20Churachandpur%20to%20Leimakhong%20was%20confronted%20by%20an%20enraged%20mob.%20The%20mob%20forcibly%20took%20away%20four%20of%20them%2C%20while%20one%20escaped.%20One%20person%20from%20the%20group%20was%20later%20rescued%20by%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Manipur%20Police%20(%40manipur_police)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanipur_police%2Fstatus%2F1721977018101936457%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fabductions-gunfight-mark-tense-day-in-manipur-9017843%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20alleged%20that%20the%20Meitei%20radical%20group%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20was%20behind%20the%20abduction.%20The%20Forum%20urged%20central%20security%20forces%20to%20launch%20search%20operations%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20fear%20they%20may%20have%20been%20killed%20or%20being%20tortured%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20was%20reported%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20in%20the%20Kangchup%20Chingkhong%20village%20when%20five%20civilians%20in%20a%20Bolero%20car%20were%20stopped%20at%20a%20security%20checkpost.%20Soon%20a%20mob%20appeared%20and%20abducted%20the%20four%2C%20including%20two%20women.%20The%20central%20security%20forces%20deployed%20there%20could%20only%20rescue%20one%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmother-3-family-members-of-soldier-abducted-by-mob-in-mani