2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333530%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wondering%20how%20to%20protect%20your%20plants%20in%20winter%3F%20Gardener%20Yashika%20shares%20easy%20gardening%20tips%20to%20ensure%20your%20plants%20continue%20to%20flourish%20this%20cold%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333530%2Fwinter-gardening-tips-how-to-protect-plants-from-cold-weather%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bulbs%20That%20Act%20As%20Inverters%3A%20Class%2012%20Student%20Lights%20Up%20Rural%20India%20With%20His%20Innovation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20residents%20of%20Bichpuri%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20financial%20literacy%20programme%20by%20a%20teenager%20turned%20into%20a%20harbinger%20of%20hope%20a%20few%20months%20later.%20After%20his%20Class%2010%20board%20exams%2C%20Uday%20Bhatia%20visited%20Bichpuri%20as%20a%20volunteer%20with%20the%20Aasra%20Foundation%20in%20April%202022%20for%20a%202-day%20programme.%20Those%2048%20hours%20left%20a%20deep%20impact%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327322%2Fretired-brigadier-p-ganesham-mentors-padma-president-award-winning-innovations-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20resident.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20to%20the%20children%20about%20their%20life%2C%20he%20found%20that%20the%20biggest%20problem%20they%20faced%20were%20frequent%20power%20outages%2C%20which%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20study.%20Hearing%20that%20a%20basic%20necessity%20like%20electricity%2C%20which%20we%20take%20for%20granted%2C%20is%20not%20available%20for%208-10%20hours%20daily%2C%20really%20shook%20Uday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20back%20to%20Delhi%20and%20dove%20deep%20into%20the%20problem.%20He%20found%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%C2%A0%20Uttarakhand%20are%20reeling%20under%20a%20power%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Moneycontrol%20report%2C%20Uttarakhand%20faced%20a%20shortfall%20of%2018%20million%20units%20of%20electricity%20everyday%20in%20January%202023%2C%20which%20was%2040%20percent%20of%20the%20daily%20demand.%20Several%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20face%20daily%20power%20cuts%20from%20anywhere%20between%20four%20to%20almost%20eight%20to%20nine%20hours%20a%20day%20in%20some%20remote%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUday%20soon%20understood%20that%20residents%20of%20villages%20like%20Bichpuri%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20financial%20means%20to%20afford%20appliances%20like%20inverters.%20He%20wanted%20to%20find%20and%20develop%20a%20solution%20for%20rural%20India%E2%80%99s%20power%20crisis.%20After%2024%20prototypes%2C%20thousands%20of%20hours%2C%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20the%2018-year-old%20built%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%93%20an%20inverter%20bulb%20that%20can%20provide%20a%20backup%20of%20almost%2010%20hours%20in%20case%20of%20a%20power%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20bulb%20that%20solves%20the%20problem.%20Speaking%20to%20those%20young%20children%20and%20seeing%20their%20troubles%20really%20moved%20me.%20Reading%20about%20the%20heat%20crisis%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20motivated%20me%20to%20solve%20this%20problem.%20How%20could%20they%20stay%20without%20electricity%20in%20such%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%3F%E2%80%9D%20Uday%20Bhatia%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20solution%20at%20Rs%20250%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FUday2-2-1699023289.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Uday%20worked%20on%2024%20prototypes%20o