%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCyXaBnMIgHI%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EBut%20introducing%20this%20South%20Indian%20culinary%20delight%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20was%20not%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20went%20door%20to%20door%20of%20various%20restaurants%20with%20samples%20and%20requested%20people%20to%20try%20our%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20At%20first%2C%20they%20would%20be%20reluctant.%20But%20then%20I%20would%20make%20the%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20within%20a%20few%20minutes%20and%20serve%20it%20to%20them%20with%20curry.%20Whoever%20tasted%20it%20appreciated%20the%20quality%20and%20the%20taste%20of%20my%20%3Cem%3Eparathas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Soon%2C%20many%20more%20people%20started%20adding%20this%20dish%20to%20their%20menus%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriced%20at%20Rs%2060%20and%20Rs%20100%2C%20these%20packaged%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3Es%20come%20in%20packs%20of%20five%20or%2010%20pieces.%20They%20have%20a%20shelf%20life%20of%20three%20days%2C%20which%20extends%20up%20to%20seven%20days%20if%20stored%20in%20refrigerators.